var book = {
	"name": "Nongbishar",
	"numChapters": 21,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hadien ka jingïap u Joshua, ki Israel ki la ïakylli ïa U Trai, ki da ong, “Uei un leit kiew nyngkong na ka bynta jong ngi pyrshah ïa ki Kanaan, ban ïaleh ïa ki?”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te U Trai u la ong, “U Judah un leit kiew: ha khmih, nga la ai noh ïa kata ka ri ha ka kti jong u.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Judah u la ong ha u Simeon u para jong u, “To ïawan kiew lem bad nga sha ka bynta jong nga, ba ngin ïaleh ïa ki Kanaan; nga ruh kumjuh ngan leit bad me sha ka bynta jong me.” Kumta, u Simeon u la leit lem bad u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Judah u la leit kiew; bad U Trai u la aiti ïa ki Kanaan bad ïa ki Peris ha ka kti jong ki: bad ki la pynïap na ki ha Besek shiphew hajar ki rangbah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ki la shem ïa u Adoni-besek ha Besek: bad ki la ïaleh ïa u bad ki la pynïap ïa ki Kanaan bad ïa ki Peris.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei u Adoni-besek u la phet ïap; ki te ki la beh ïa u, bad ki la kem ïa u, bad ki la ot noh ïa ki 'ti kmie bad ïa ki 'jat kmie jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Adoni-besek te u la ong, “Hynñiewphew ki syiem, ba la ot noh ïa ki 'ti kmie bad ïa ki 'jat kmie jong ki, ki la ju khar ïa la ka jingbam hapoh ka miej jong nga: kumba nga la leh, kumta U Blei u la leh kylliang ïa nga.” Te ki la wallam ïa u sha Jerusalem, bad hangta u la ïap.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ki khun u Judah ki la ïaleh ïa ka Jerusalem, bad ki la jop ïa ka, bad ki la pom ïa ka da ka syrti waitlam, bad ki la wiang ding ïa ka shnong.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te hadien kata, ki khun u Judah ki la leit hiar ïaleh thma ïa ki Kanaan kiba la shong ha ka ri lum, bad ha kaba shathie, bad ha ka ri them.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Judah u la leit ïaleh ïa ki Kanaan kiba shong ha Hebron: (te ka kyrteng ka Hebron mynshuwa ka la long “ka Kiriath-arba”): bad ki la pynïap ïa u Sheshai, bad u Ahiman, bad u Talmai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te nangta u la leit ïaleh ïa ki nong Debir: (te ka kyrteng ka Debir mynshuwa ka la long “ka Kiriath-sepher”).",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Kaleb u la ong, “Jar uba ïaleh ïa ka Kiriath-sepher, bad uba jop ïa ka, ïa u ngan pynbuh kurim bad ka Akhsah ka khun jong nga.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Othniel u khun u Kenas, u hynbew jong u Kaleb, u la jop ïa ka: te u la pynbuh kurim bad u ïa ka Akhsah ka khun jong u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ynda ka la wan ha u, ka la kyntu ïa u ban pan na u kpa jong ka, ïa kawei ka khyndew: bad ka la hiar noh nalor la ka kadda; u Kaleb te u la ong ha ka, “Pha kwah aïu?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ka te ka la ong ha u, “To ai jingkyrkhu ïa nga; naba me la ai ha nga ka ri shathie, to ai ruh ha nga ki umpohliew:” bad u Kaleb u la ai ha ka, ïa kita ki umpohliew kiba haneng bad kita ki umpohliew kiba harum.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki khun u Ken, u kthaw kurim jong u Moses, ki la ïaleit kiew na ka nongbah ki dieng Tlai, lem bad ki khun u Judah sha ka ri khlaw Judah, kaba shaphang shathie jong ka Arad; bad ki la ïaleit shong ruh bad kita ki briew.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Judah u la leit bad u Simeon u para jong u, bad ki la ïa-pynïap ïa ki Kanaan kiba shong ha Sephath, bad ki la pynduh khoit ïa ka. Bad ïa ka kyrteng kata ka shnong la khot “ka Hormah”.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki Judah ruh ki la jop ïa ka Gasa bad ïa ki phang jong ka, bad ka Ashkelon bad ki phang jong ka, bad ka Ekron bad ki phang jong ka.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U Trai te u la don bad ki Judah; bad ki la jop ïa ki riewlum; naba kim lah ban beh noh ïa kiba shong ha ka ri them, namar ki la don ki kali nar.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ki la ai ïa ka Hebron ha u Kaleb, kumba u Moses u la kren: bad u la beh noh nangta ïa ki lai ngut ki khun u Anak.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki khun u Benjamin kim shym la beh noh ïa ki Jebus kiba shong ha Jerusalem: hynrei, ki Jebus ki la shong lem bad ki khun u Benjamin ha Jerusalem haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ka ïing u Joseph de, ki ruh ki la kiew ban ïaleh ïa ka Bethel: bad U Trai u la long lem bad ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ka ïing u Joseph ka la phah syntiat ïa ka Bethel. (Te ka kyrteng kata ka shnong mynshuwa ka la long “ka Lus”).",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te kita ki nongsyntiat ki la ïohi ïa u briew ba u mih noh na kata ka shnong, bad ki la ong ha u, “Pyni ïa ngi, ngi kyrpad ïa me, ïa ka lynti ban rung sha shnong, bad ngi ruh ngin leh sbun ïa me.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ynda u la pyni ïa ki, ïa ka lynti sha shnong, ki la pom ïa kata ka shnong da ka syrti waitlam; hynrei, ki la pyllait ïa uta u briew bad ka ïing jong u baroh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Uta u briew te u la leit sha ka ri ki Hit, bad u la thaw kawei ka shnong, bad u la khot ïa ka kyrteng jong ka, “ka Lus”: kaba long ka kyrteng jong ka, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ki Manasseh ruh kim shym la beh noh ïa ki nong Beth-shean bad ïa ki shnong jong ka, lymne ïa ki nong Taanakh bad ki shnong jong ka, lymne ïa ki nong Dor bad ki shnong jong ka, lymne ïa ki nong Ibleam bad ki shnong jong ka, lymne ki nong Megiddo bad ki shnong jong ka: hynrei, ki Kanaan ki shu shong ha kata ka ri.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hynrei, ynda ki Israel ki la kham khraw bor, ki pyntrei shitom ïa ki Kanaan, te kim shym la beh noh khoit ïa ki.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ki Ephraim ruh kim shym la beh noh ïa ki Kanaan kiba shong ha Geser; hynrei, ki Kanaan ki la shong ha Geser hapdeng jong ki.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ki Sabulon kim shym la beh noh ïa ki nong Kitron, lymne ïa ki nong Nahalol; hynrei, ki Kanaan ki shong hapdeng jong ki, bad ki la siew khajna.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ki Asher ruh kim shym la beh noh ïa ki nong Akko, lymne ïa ki nong Sidon, lymne ïa ki nong Ahlab, lymne ïa ki nong Akhsib, lymne ïa ki nong Helbah, lymne ïa ki nong Aphik, lymne ïa ki nong Rehob:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> hynrei, ki Asher ki la shong hapdeng ki Kanaan, ki trai kata ka ri: namar kim shym la beh noh ïa ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ki Naphtali kim shym beh noh ïa ki nong Beth-shemesh, lymne ki nong Beth-anath; hynrei, ki la shong hapdeng ki Kanaan, ki trai kata ka ri: pynban, ki nong Beth-shemesh bad ki nong Beth-anath ki la siew khajna ha ki.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ki Amor te ki la beh ïa ki khun u Dan sha ri lum: naba kim shah ïa ki ban wan hiar sha ka ri them:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> hynrei, ki Amor ki shu shong ha u lum Heres, ha Aijalon, bad ha Shaalbim, pynban, ka kti ka ïing u Joseph ka la lah, bad kumta ki la siew khajna.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad ka pud ki Amor ka la long naduh ka thiep Akrabbim, naduh uta u mawsiang, bad shaneng."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u angel U Trai u la wan kiew na Gilgal sha Bokhim. Bad u la ong, “Nga la pynmih noh ïa phi na ka ri Ijipt, bad nga la wallam ïa phi sha ka ri kaba nga la smai ha ki kpa jong phi; bad nga la ong, ‘Ngan ym pynkheiñ ïa ka jutang jong nga bad phi lano lano:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad phin ym ïateh jutang bad ki briew jong kane ka ri; phin pynkyllon ïa ki duwan jong ki:’ hynrei, phim shym la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong nga: balei phi la leh ïa kane?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Namar kata, nga ruh nga la ong, ‘Ngan ym beh noh ïa kine na khmat jong phi; hynrei, kin long kum ki shiah ha ki krung jong phi, bad ki blei jong ki kin long jingriam ïa phi.’ ”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba uta u angel U Trai u la kren ïa kine ki ktien ha ki khun Israel baroh, u paidbah u la kyang jam, bad u la ïam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki la kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “ka Bokhim” bad ki la kñia hangta ha U Trai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba u Joshua u la phah noh ïa u paidbah, ki khun Israel ki la ïaleit uwei uwei baroh sha la ka jong ka ri kynti ban ïoh ïa kata ka ri.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u paidbah u la shakri ïa U Trai baroh ki sngi jong u Joshua, bad baroh ki sngi jong ki tymmen basan kiba la im palat ïa u Joshua, kiba la ïohi ïa ka kam bakhraw jong U Trai, kaba u la lah leh na ka bynta ki Israel.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Joshua u khun u Nun, u shakri U Trai, u la ïap noh, haba u la long shispah shiphew snem ka rta.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki la tep ïa u ha ka rud ka ri kynti jong u ha Timnath-heres, ha ka ri lum Ephraim, shaphang shatei jong u lum Gaash.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ïa kata ka pateng bynriew ruh baroh la ïalum lang ha ki kpa jong ki: te la mih kawei pat ka pateng bynriew hadien jong ki, ka bym shym la ithuh ïa U Trai, lymne ïa ka kam ruh kaba u la leh na ka bynta ki Israel.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la leh ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, bad ki la leit shakri ïa ki Baal:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad ki la lyndet ïa U Trai, uba U Blei ki kpa jong ki, uba la wallam noh ïa ki na ka ri Ijipt, bad ki la ïabud ïa kiwei pat ki blei, na ki blei jong ki bynriew kiba don baroh sawdong ïa ki, bad ki la dem ngon ha ki: bad ki la pynkhih bitar ïa U Trai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki la lyndet te ïa U Trai, bad ki la leit shakri ïa u Baal bad ïa ka Ashtaroth.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hangta, ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh pyrshah ïa ki Israel, bad u la ai noh ïa ki ha ki kti ki nonglute kiba la lute ïa ki, bad u la die noh ïa ki ha ki kti ki nongshun jong ki baroh sawdong, ba kumta kim lah shuh ban ïeng ha khmat ki nongshun jong ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kat shaba ki la mih, ka kti U Trai ka la long pyrshah ïa ki, ïa ka ban sniew, kumba U Trai u la lah kren, bad kumba u la lah smai ha ki: te la pynjynjar sat ïa ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te U Trai u la pynmih ki nongbishar, kiba la pyllait ïa ki na ka kti jong kita kiba la lute ïa ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te pynban, kim shym la shahshkor ïa ki nongbishar jong ki, naba ki la ïaleit ïaklim bad kiwei pat ki blei, bad ki la dem ngon ha ki: ki la phai sharud kloi kloi na kata ka lynti ha kaba ki kpa jong ki, ki la ïaid, haba ki da kohnguh ïa ki hukum jong U Trai: hynrei, ki kim shym la leh kumta.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba U Trai u la pynmih ki nongbishar ïa ki, ynda kumta, U Trai u la don lem bad uta u nongbishar, bad u la pyllait ïa ki na ka kti ki nongshun jong ki baroh ki sngi jong uta u nongbishar: namar U Trai u la kylla-ka-bamut na ka bynta ka jingud jong ki namar kita kiba la banbeiñ ïa ki bad ba la pynshitom ïa ki.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, haba uta u nongbishar u la ïap, ki la phai dien, bad ki la nang kham leh sniew ban ïa ki kpa jong ki, ha kaba bud ïa kiwei pat ki blei ban leit shakri ïa ki, bad ban dem ngon ha ki; kim shym la phai noh na la ki jingleh, lymne na ka lynti bamutlop jong ki.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh pyrshah ïa ki khun Israel; bad u la ong, “Namar ba kane ka jaid bynriew ka la ryngkang ïa ka jutang jong nga kaba nga la hukum ïa ki kpa jong ki, bad kim shym la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong nga;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> nga ruh ngan ym beh noh shuh ïano ïano na khmat jong ki na kita ki jaid bynriew ïa kiba u Joshua u la pynsah mynba u la ïap:”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> ba da kita nga lah ban tynjuh ïa ki Israel, la kin sumar ne em ïa ka lynti U Trai ban ïaid ha ka, kumba ki kpa jong ki, ki la sumar ïa ka.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, U Trai u la pynsah ïa kita ki jaid bynriew, um da pynkloi ban beh noh ïa ki; lymne um shym la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti u Joshua."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kine te ki long ki jaid bynriew kiba U Trai u la pynsah, ban tynjuh ïa ki Israel da ki, wat kita baroh ki bym shym la tip ïa kita ki thma ka ri Kanaan baroh;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> tang ba kita ki pateng bynriew ki khun Israel kin ïoh tip, ban hikai ïapom ïa ki, kita keiñ ki bym shym la tip satia ïa kane mynshuwa;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ki san doloi ki Philistia, ki Kanaan baroh, bad ki Sidon, bad ki Hib kiba shong ha u lum Lebanon, naduh u lum Baal-hermon haduh ka lynti sha Hamath.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kine ki la sah ban tynjuh ïa ki Israel da ki, ban tip la kin shahshkor ne em ïa ki hukum U Trai, kiba u la hukum ïa ki kpa jong ki da ka kti u Moses.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la shong hapdeng ki Kanaan; ki Hit, bad ki Amor, bad ki Peris, bad ki Hib, bad ki Jebus:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad ki la shim ïa ki khun kynthei jong ki ban long ki tnga jong ki, ki la ai ruh ïa la ki khun kynthei ha ki khun shynrang jong ki, bad ki la shakri ïa ki blei jong ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la leh ïa ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, bad ki la klet ïa U Trai U Blei jong ki, bad ki la leit shakri ïa ki Baal bad ki Asheroth.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Namar kata, ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh ïa ki Israel, bad u la die noh ïa ki ha ka kti u Kushan-rishathaim u syiem ka Mesopotamia: bad ki khun Israel ki la shakri ïa u Kushan-rishathaim, phra snem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba ki khun Israel ki la lynñiar ha U Trai, U Trai u la pynmih ïa u nongpynim ïa ki khun Israel, uba la pyllait ïa ki, u Othniel keiñ u khun u Kenas, u hynbew u Kaleb.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Mynsiem U Trai te u la wan ha u, bad u la bishar ïa ki Israel; bad u la mih ha ka thma, U Trai te u la ai noh ïa u Kushan-rishathaim u syiem ka Mesopotamia ha ka kti jong u: bad ka kti jong u ka la jop ïa u Kushan-rishathaim.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka ri ruh ka la suk sawphew snem. Bad u Othniel u khun u Kenas u la ïap.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la leh ïa ka basniew pat ha khmat U Trai: bad U Trai u la ai bor ïa u Eglon u syiem ka Moab ban ïaleh ïa ki Israel, namar ba ki la leh ïa ka basniew ha khmat U Trai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la ïalum ha u ïa ki khun u Ammon bad u Amalek; te u la leit bad u la jop ïa ki Israel, bad ki la ïoh ïa ka nongbah ki dieng Tlai.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kumta, ki khun Israel ki la shakri ïa u Eglon u syiem ka Moab, khatphra snem.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, haba ki khun Israel ki la lynñiar ha U Trai, te U Trai u la pynmih ha ki u nongpyllait im, u Ehud keiñ u khun u Gera, u Benjamin, u briew uba kadiang: bad ha u ki khun Israel ki la phah ïa ka jingnguh syiem ha u Eglon u syiem ka Moab.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, u Ehud u la khreh ïa lade ka jamdor ar liang syrti, kaba jrong shi pruh; bad u la tynsat ïa ka hapoh la ki jaiñ ha ka syngkai sha kamon jong u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u la wallam ïa kata ka jingnguh syiem ha u Eglon u syiem ka Moab. Te u Eglon u la long u briew u basngaid eh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ynda u la lah ai kata ka jingnguh syiem, u la phah noh ïa kita ki briew kiba la bah ïa kata ka jingnguh syiem.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, u hi u la kylla dien pat na kita ki par kiba don hajan Gilgal, bad u la ong, “Nga don ka kam ba jar jar ha me, ko syiem.” U te u la ong, “Sngap jar.” Baroh te kiba la ïeng hajan jong u ki la mih noh na u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Ehud u la wan ha u; te u shong marwei hi ha la ka kamra pyngngad. Bad u Ehud u la ong, “Ka ktien na U Blei nga don ha me.” Bad u la ïeng joit na la ka jaka shong.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba u Ehud u la sei ïa la ka kti kadiang bad u la sei ïa ka jamdor na ka syngkai kamon jong u, u la tynrah ïa ka na ka kpoh jong u:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> te ka sping ruh ka la rung lem bad ka sla wait; bad ka khleiñ ka la dambit ha ka sla wait, naba um shym sei shuh ïa kata ka jamdor na ka kpoh jong u; te ka la pei blait shadien.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ynda kumta, u Ehud u la mih noh sha ka baranda, bad u la khang lyndet ïa ki jingkhang ka kamra, bad u la khyrwait ïa ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ynda u la lah mih noh, ki shakri jong u ki la ïawan; bad ki la ïohi, te, ha khmih, ïa ki jingkhang ka kamra la khyrwait; bad ki la ïa-ong, “Shisha u tap ïa la ki kjat ha ka kamra pyngngad.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki la ap ha ban da ki la lehrain: te, ha khmih, um shym plie shuh ïa ki jingkhang ka kamra; namar kata, ki la shim ïa u shabi bad ki la plie; te, ha khmih, u kynrad jong ki u la kyllon ïap ha tbian.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U Ehud te u la phet ïap katba ki la dang ap, bad u la palat ïa kita ki par, u la lait ruh haduh Seirath.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ynda u la lah poi, u la put ka turoi ha ka ri lum Ephraim, bad ki khun Israel ki la hiar lem bad u na ka ri lum, ma u ruh ha shuwa jong ki.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “Bud ïa nga: naba U Trai u la ai noh ïa ki Moab ki nongshun jong phi ha ka kti jong phi.” Te ki la hiar hadien jong u, bad ki la ïoh ïa ki lynti khriang ka Jordan pyrshah ïa ki Moab, bad kim shah ïano ïano ruh ban ryngkang.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ki la pynïap na ki Moab ha kata ka por kumba shiphew hajar ki rangbah, baroh ki riewkhlaiñ, bad baroh ki riewshlur; ym shym la lait uwei ruh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kumta, la jop ïa ka Moab ha kata ka sngi ha ka kti ki Israel. Ka ri te ka la suk phraphew snem.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hadien jong u te u Shamgar u khun u Anath, uba la pynïap na ki Philistia hynriewspah ki rangbah da u dieng ñiah masi: u ruh u la pyllait ïa ki Israel."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la leh ïa ka basniew pat ha khmat U Trai, ynda la ïap u Ehud.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te U Trai u la die noh ïa ki ha ka kti u Jabin u syiem ka Kanaan, uba synshar ha Hasor; u rangbah ki paidïapom jong u, u Sisera, uba shong ha Harosheth ki Jentil.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la lynñiar ha U Trai: naba u la don khyndaispah ki kali nar; bad arphew snem u la banbeiñ eh ïa ki khun Israel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ka Deborah, ka nongïathuhlypa, ka tnga u Lapidoth, ha kata ka por ka la bishar ma ka, ïa ki Israel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ka la shong hapoh u dieng Tlai jong ka Deborah hapdeng ka Ramah bad ka Bethel ha ri lum Ephraim: bad ki khun Israel ki la ju wan kiew sha ka ban ïoh bishar.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ka la phah khot ïa u Barak u khun u Abinoam na Kedesh-naphtali, bad ka la ong ha u, “Hato U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, um shym la hukum, ‘To khie, kynriah sha u lum Tabor, bad ïalam bad me shiphew hajar ngut na ki khun u Naphtali bad na ki khun u Sabulon?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ngan pynwan sha me sha ka wah Kishon ïa u Sisera, u rangbah ki paidïapom jong u Jabin, lem bad ki kali jong u bad u paidbah jong u de; bad ngan ai noh ïa u ha ka kti jong me.’ ”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Barak u la ong ha ka, “Lada phan leit lem bad nga, te ngan leit keiñ: hynrei, lada pha phan ym leit lem bad nga, ngan ym leit.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka te ka la ong, “Ïa ka ban leit ngan leit lem bad me: pynban, men ym ïoh burom ma me na kane ka jingleit kaba me leit: naba U Trai un die noh ïa u Sisera ha ka kti ka kynthei.” Ka Deborah te ka la ïeng, bad ka la leit lem bad u Barak sha Kedesh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Barak u la khot lang ïa ki Sabulon bad ki Naphtali sha Kedesh; bad ki la leit kiew shiphew hajar ki rangbah ha ki sla'jat jong u: ka Deborah de ka la leit lem bad u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Heber u nong Ken u la pynkhlad ïa lade na ki Ken, wat na ki khun u Hobab u kthaw kurim u Moses, bad u la pynïeng ïa la ka ïingjaiñ haduh uta u dieng Sning ha Saanannim, uba hajan Kedesh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki la ïathuh te ha u Sisera ba u Barak u khun u Abinoam u la leit kiew sha u lum Tabor.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, u Sisera u la ïalum lang ïa la ki kali baroh, kita ki khyndaispah ki kali nar keiñ, bad u paidbah baroh uba la don lem bad u, naduh Harosheth jong ki Jentil, haduh ka wah Kishon.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ka Deborah ka la ong ha u Barak, “Ïeng joit; naba kane ka long kata ka sngi ba U Trai u la ai noh ïa u Sisera ha ka kti jong me: hato U Trai um shym la leit ha shuwa jong me?” Kumta, u Barak u la leit hiar na u lum Tabor, bad shiphew hajar ki rangbah ki ïabud ïa u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad U Trai u la pynduh khoit ïa u Sisera, bad ki kali jong u baroh, bad u paidïapom jong u baroh, da ka syrti waitlam ha khmat u Barak; te u Sisera u la hiar noh na la ka kali, bad u la phet ïap noh da ki kjat.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, u Barak u la beh ïa kita ki kali, bad ïa uta u paidïapom haduh ka Harosheth ki Jentil: bad uta u paidïapom jong u Sisera baroh u la kyllon da ka syrti waitlam; uwei ruh ym shym pynsah shuh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, u Sisera u la phet ïap noh da ki kjat sha ka ïingjaiñ ka Jael ka tnga u Heber u nong Ken: namar la don ka jingïasuk hapdeng u Jabin u syiem ka Hasor bad ka ïing u Heber u nong Ken.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka Jael ka la leit tan ïa u Sisera, bad ka la ong ha u, “To ale sha ïing, kynrad, ale sha nga; wat sheptieng.” Te ynda u la rung sha ka shapoh ka ïingjaiñ, ka la pyntap ïa u da ka banat.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U la ong te ha ka, “Ai ha nga, nga kyrpad ïa pha, khyndiat ka um ban dih; naba nga sliang.” Te ka la law shi bitor ka dud, bad ka la pyndih ïa u, bad ka la pyntap ïa u ruh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U te u la ong ha ka, “To ïeng ha jingkhang ka ïingjaiñ, te haba wan mano mano ba kylli ïa pha, da kaba ong, ‘Don uno uno hangne?’ te phan ong, ‘Em.’ ”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, ka Jael ka tnga u Heber ka la shim u snar ïingjaiñ, bad u tyrnem ha la ka kti, bad ka la leit mian mian sha u, bad ka la sah ïa uta u snar na ki moi moi jong u, bad u la pei lyngba ruh sha ka khyndew; naba u la thiah lyngngai; kumta u la thiah lter bad u la ïap noh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te, ha khmih, katba u Barak u nang beh ïa u Sisera, ka Jael ka la wan tan ïa u, bad ka la ong ha u, “Ale, te ngan pyni ha me ïa uta u briew ïa uba me wad.” Bad u la wan sha ka; te, ha khmih, u Sisera u la thiah ïap, bad uta u snar ha ki moi moi jong u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, U Blei u la jop ha kata ka sngi ïa u Jabin u syiem ka Kanaan ha khmat ki khun Israel.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ka kti ki khun Israel ka la nang jop nang jop ïa u Jabin u syiem ka Kanaan, ha ban da ki la pynduh khoit ïa u Jabin u syiem ka Kanaan."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, ka Deborah bad u Barak u khun u Abinoam ki la ïarwai ha kata ka sngi, ki da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To ïaroh phi ïa U Trai, naba ki nongïalam ki la ïalam ha Israel, naba ki paidbah ki la ai sngewbha ïa lade.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “To sngew, ko phi ki syiem; to shahshkor, ko phi ki bakhraw batri; ma nga hi ngan rwai ha U Trai; ngan rwai ïaroh ïa U Trai, uba U Blei ki Israel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “A Trai, mynba me la mih noh na Seir, mynba me la ïaid na ka lyngkha Edom, ka khyndew ka la khynñiuh, bad ki bneng ki la jaw, ki lyoh ki la pynjaw ka um keiñ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ki lum ki la um noh ha khmat U Trai, wat uta u Sinai ha khmat U Trai, uba U Blei ki Israel.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Ha ki sngi u Shamgar u khun u Anath, ha ki sngi ka Jael, ym don ba ïaid na ki lynti bah, ki nongleit jingleit ki la ïaid na ki lynti khlaw.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki nongsynshar ki la duh ha Israel, ki la duh keiñ, tad ynda nga la ïeng ma nga ka Deborah, ba nga la ïeng ban long kmie keiñ ha Israel.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ki la shim da ki blei thymmai; hangta te la don thma ha ki khyrdop: la ju ïohi mo ïa ka stieh lane ïa u sum hapdeng ki sawphew hajar ngut ha Israel?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka dohnud jong nga ka long sha ki nongsynshar ki Israel, kiba la ai sngewbha ïa lade hapdeng u paidbah. To kyrkhu phi ïa U Trai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “To ïalap phi, kiba shong halor ki kadda lieh, phi kiba shong halor ki stranji bakordor, bad phi kiba ïaid ha ka lynti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Jngai na ka jingrisa ki nongsiat khnam, ha ki jaka tong um, hangta kin ïalap ïa ki kam bahok jong U Trai, ki kam bahok jong ka jingsynshar jong U ha Israel. “Ynda kumta, ki paidbah U Trai ki la hiar sha ki khyrdop.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “To khie, to khie, ko Deborah; to khie, to khie, to thaw ka jingrwai: to ïeng, ko Barak, bad ïa kita ba la kem mraw to ïalam mraw, me u khun u Abinoam.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, la wan hiar kiba dang sah na ki rangbah bad u paidbah; U Trai u la wan hiar na ka bynta jong nga ban ïaleh ïa ki bakhrawbor.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na u Ephraim ki la wan hiar kita kiba u thied jong ki u long ha u Amalek; hadien jong me, u Benjamin, hapdeng ki paidbah jong me; na u Makhir la wan hiar ki nongsynshar, bad na u Sabulon kita kiba bat u dieng u nongïalam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ki rangbah u Issakhar te ki la don lem bad ka Deborah; kumba la long u Issakhar, kumta u la long u Barak: sha ka them ki la tur noh ha ki kjat jong u. Ha ki lynti um u Reuben la don kiba jur ki jingthmu ka dohnud.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Balei me shong hapdeng ki jingker langbrot, ban sngap ïa ki jingput ïa ki kynhun? Ha ki lynti um u Reuben la don kiba jur ki jingïit ka dohnud.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ka Gilead ka la shong sha lyndet ka Jordan: bad u Dan, balei ba u la sah ha ki lieng? u Asher u la shong khop harud ka duriaw, bad u la shong ha ki kdong um jong u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Sabulon u la long u paidbah ba la kheiñduh ïa la ka mynsiem jin haduh ka jingïap, u Naphtali ruh, ha ki jaka bajrong jong ka ri.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Ki syiem ki la wan bad ki la ïaleh; ynda kumta, ki syiem ka Kanaan ki la ïaleh thma na Taanakh harud ki um Megiddo: kim shym la ïohnong da u sbai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ki la ïaleh na bneng, ki khlur ha la ki jingïaid ki la ïaleh thma pyrshah ïa u Sisera.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ka wah Kishon ka la rong noh ïa ki, kata ka wah barim, ka wah Kishon keiñ. Ko mynsiem jong nga to nang ïaid da ka bor.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Hangta, ki khnap kulai ki la kyrdem namar ki jingrynsied, ki jingrynsied kiba khlaiñ jong ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “To tim phi ïa ka Meros,” la ong u angel U Trai, “to tim duh phi ïa ki briew jong ka; namar kim shym la wan ban ïarap ïa U Trai, ban ïarap ïa U Trai pyrshah ïa ki bakhlaiñ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> “Kan long kaba suk ka Jael, ka tnga u Heber u nong Ken, nalor ki kynthei, kan long kaba suk ma ka nalor ki kynthei ha ka ïingjaiñ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U la pan ka um, te ka la ai ïa u da ka dud; ha ka pliang kaba kor ka la wallam makhon ïa u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ka la buh ïa la ka kti ha u snar, bad ka kti kamon jong ka ha u tyrnem ki nongtrei; bad da uta u tyrnem ka la sah ïa u Sisera, ka la sah lyngba na ka khlieh jong u, ka la sam keiñ bad ka la sah lyngba ïa ki moi moi jong u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ha ki kjat jong ka u la dem, u la kyllon, u la thiah: ha ki kjat jong ka u la dem, u la kyllon: ha kaba u la dem, hangta u la kyllon ïap.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Lyngba ki jingkhang ïit ka la jngoh, bad ka la pyrta, ka kmie u Sisera ka la pyrta lyngba ka phrah, ‘Ka slem lei katta ka kali jong u ban wan? ki tud lei ki shalyntem ki kali jong u?’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ki lok kynthei bastad jong ka ki la ïathuh ïa ka, ka ruh ka la phai ktien ha lade hi,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ‘Hato kim shym la shem kim shym la ïabynta ïa ka jinglute? ha uwei uwei kawei lane ar ki samla; ha u Sisera ka jinglute ki jaiñkup bun rong, ka jinglute bun rong ka jingsuh thoh, baroh ar liang ka jingsuh thoh ba bun rong, ha ki ryndang jong ka jinglute?’",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Kumta ai kin jot ki nongshun jong me baroh, A Trai: hynrei, ai ba kita kiba ieit ïa U kin long kum ka sngi haba ka dang ïeng ha ka bor jong ka.” Ka ri te ka la suk sawphew snem."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la leh ïa ka basniew ha khmat U Trai: bad U Trai u la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti ki Midian hynñiew snem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka kti ki Midian te ka la jop ïa ki Israel: bad na ka bynta ki Midian, ki khun Israel ki la thaw ïa lade ïa kita ki thliew kiba ha ki lum, bad ïa kita ki krem, bad ïa ki kut baskhem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Haba ki Israel te ki la bet, kita ki Midian ki la wan kiew, bad ki Amalek, bad ki khun mihngi; kita, ki la wan kiew pyrshah ïa ki;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad ki la sher dara pyrshah ïa ki, bad ki la pynduh ïa ka jingmih ka khyndew, haduh ba me poi sha Gasa, bad kim shym la iehnoh jingbam shuh ïa ki Israel, lymne langbrot, lymne masi, lymne kadda.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Naba ki la wan kiew lem bad la ki jingri bad la ki ïingjaiñ, bad ki la wan kiew u paidbah kum ki puit; ïa ki hi bad ki ut jong ki ym lah kheiñ shuh: bad ki la wan bsut sha ka ri ban pynjot ïa ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ki Israel te ki la shipa eh na ka bynta ki Midian: bad ki khun Israel ki la lynñiar ha U Trai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba ki khun Israel ki la lynñiar ha U Trai na ka bynta ki Midian,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Trai u la phah ïa u nongïathuhlypa ha ki khun Israel: bad u la ong ha ki, “Kumne u ong U Trai, U Blei jong ki Israel: ‘Nga la wallam noh ïa phi na ka ri Ijipt, bad nga la pynmih noh ïa phi na ka ïing ka jinglongmraw;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad nga la pyllait ïa phi na ka kti ki Ijipt, bad na ka kti kita baroh kiba la banbeiñ ïa phi, nga la beh ruh ïa ki na khmat jong phi, bad nga la ai ha phi ïa ka ri jong ki;’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> nga la ong de ha phi: ‘Nga long U Trai uba U Blei jong phi; phin ym sheptieng ïa ki blei ki Amor, ha ka ri jong kiba phi shong’; hynrei, phim shym la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong nga.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, u angel U Trai u la wan, bad u la shong hapoh uta u dieng Sning uba ha Ophrah, uba dei ïa u Joash u nong Abieser; te u khun jong u, u Gideon u dang shoh Kew ha ka jaka khem umsoh, ban buhrieh ïa u na ki Midian.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u angel U Trai u la paw ha u, bad u la ong ha u, “U Trai u don ryngkat bad me, me u briew uba shynrang.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U Gideon te u la ong ha u, “A kynrad jong nga, lada U Trai u don ryngkat bad ngi, balei te ba kane baroh ka la ngat ha ngi? bad shano ki kam phylla jong U baroh kiba ki kpa jong ngi ki la ïathuh ha ngi, ki da ong, ‘U Trai um shym la wallam noh ïa ngi na ka ri Ijipt?’ hynrei mynta, U Trai u la lyndet noh ïa ngi, bad U la ai noh ïa ngi ha ka kti ki Midian.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Trai te U la peit ha u, bad U la ong, “Khie leit ha kane ka bor jong me, bad pyllait ïa ki Israel na ka kti ki Midian: ngam shym la phah ma nga ïa me?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U te u la ong ha U, “A Trai, kumno ngan pyllait ïa ki Israel? ha khmih, ka kur jong nga ka baduk tam ha Manasseh, bad nga ruh u barit tam ha ka ïing u kpa jong nga.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U Trai te U la ong ha u, “Shisha ngan long lem bad me, bad men jop ïa ki Midian kum ïa uwei u briew.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U la ong te ha U, “Lada kumta nga la shem sngewbha ha khmat jong me, to men pyni ka dak ha nga ba long ma me uba kren bad nga.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nga kyrpad ïa me, wat leit noh nangne, tad ynda nga wan ha me, bad nga wallam ka jingainguh jong nga ban buh ha khmat jong me.” U te u la ong, “Ngan ap keiñ haduh ba men da wan pat.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u Gideon u la rung shapoh, bad u la pynkhreh ïa u khun blang, bad ïa ki 'pu stang khlem thiat da shi ephah u 'purew: ïa ka doh u la buh ha ka tukri, bad u la buh ïa ka syrwa ha u khiew, bad u la wallam ïa ka ha u hapoh uta u dieng Sning, bad u la ai ïa ka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U angel U Blei te u la ong ha u, “To shim ïa kata ka doh bad ïa ki kpu khlem thiat, bad buh ïa ki halor une u mawsiang, bad to theh ïa kata ka syrwa.” Te u la leh kumta.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, u angel U Trai u la rah ïa ka tduh jong u diengduh uba ha ka kti jong u, u la pyndei ha kata ka doh bad ha ki kpu khlem thiat; te ka ding ka la mih na uta u mawsiang, bad ka la pyning duh ïa ka doh bad ïa ki kpu khlem thiat; hadien kata, u angel U Trai u la leit noh na khmat jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te haba u Gideon u la sngewthuh ba u la long u angel U Trai, u Gideon u la ong, “Wa, A Trai uba U Blei! namar nga la ïohi markhmat ïa u angel U Trai.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U Trai te U la ong ha u, “To long suk ma me; wat sheptieng: men ym ïap.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ynda kumta, u Gideon u la tei ka duwan ha U Trai hangta, bad u la khot ïa ka “Jehobah-shalom:” (Haduh kane ka sngi ka dang don ha Ophrah jong ki Abieser.)",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ha kata ka miet, U Trai u la ong ha u, “To shim ïa u masi dab u kpa jong me, u masi dab u ba-ar keiñ! u bahynñiew snem ka rta, bad to pynkyllon ïa ka duwan jong u Baal kaba u kpa jong me u don, to pynduh ruh ïa ka Asherah kaba ha ka:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad to tei ïa ka duwan ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong me ha kliar kane ka kut, ha ka rukom ba la buh beit, bad to shim ïa uta u masi dab u ba-ar, bad to ainguh ka jingainguh thang da kita ki dieng jong kata ka Asherah ïa kiba men sa pynduh.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda kumta, u Gideon u la shim shiphew ngut na ki shakri jong u, bad u la leh kumba U Trai u la kren ha u: te namar ba u la sheptieng ïa ki kur u kpa jong u bad ïa ki rangbah kata ka shnong, um lah ban leh mynsngi, u la leh mynmiet.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te haba ki rangbah ka shnong ki la khie dang step phyrngab, ha khmih, ïa ka duwan u Baal la pynkyllon, bad ïa ka Asherah kaba ha ka la pynduh noh, bad ïa u masi dab u ba-ar de la kñia halor kata ka duwan ba la tei.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ki la ïa-ong paralok te, “Uei ba la leh ïa kane?” Haba ki la wad te bad kylli, ki la ïa-ong, “U Gideon u khun u Joash u la leh ïa kane.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ynda kumta, ki rangbah ka shnong ki la ong ha u Joash, “Wallam noh ïa u khun jong me, ba un ïap: naba u la pynkyllon ïa ka duwan u Baal, bad naba u la pynduh noh ïa ka Asherah kaba ha ka.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> U Joash te u la ong ha kita baroh ba ïeng ïaleh ïa u, “Phin ïasaid na ka bynta u Baal? lane phin pynim ïa u? uta uba ïasaid na ka bynta jong u, to ai ba un ïap ha kane ka step: lada u long u blei, to ai un ïasaid na ka bynta ïa lade, namar ba don uba la pynkyllon ïa ka duwan jong u.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Namar kata, ha kata ka sngi u la khot “Jerubbaal” ïa u, u da ong, “Ai u Baal un ïasaid pyrshah ïa u,” namar ba u la pynkyllon ïa ka duwan jong u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ki Midian baroh bad ki Amalek bad ki khun mihngi ki la ïalum lang; bad ki la leit sha shiliang, bad ki la sher dara ha ka them Jesril.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, U Mynsiem U Trai u la wan ha u Gideon; bad u la put ka turoi; te ki Abieser ki la ïalang hadien jong u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U la phah te ki nonglam-ktien ha ki Manasseh baroh; ki ruh ki la ïalang hadien jong u: bad u la phah ki nonglam-ktien ha ki Asher, bad ha ki Sabulon, bad ha ki Naphtali; ki de ki la wan kiew ban tan ïa u.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te u Gideon u la ong ha U Blei, “Lada men pynim ïa ki Israel da ka kti jong nga, kumba me la kren,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> ha khmih, ngan buh u 'ñiuh langbrot ha ka kyntem; lada ka umjer kan don tang ha u shñiuh hi, bad kan rkhiang ha ka khyndew baroh, te ngan tip ba men pynim ïa ki Israel da ka kti jong nga, kumba me la kren.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te ka la long kumta, naba u la khie dang step ha kaba lashai, bad u la lum ïa u shñiuh, bad u la khyrwait ïa ka umjer na uta u shñiuh, shi khuri dap ka um.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te u Gideon u la ong ha U Blei, “Wat ai ba ka jingbitar jong me kan meh ïa nga, bad ngan kren sa kane shi sien: nga kyrpad ïa me, ai ngan tynjuh da une u shñiuh sa kane shi sien; ai kan rkhiang tang ha une u shñiuh, bad ha ka khyndew baroh kan long umjer.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad U Blei u la leh kumta ha kata ka miet: naba ka la rkhiang tang u shñiuh hi, hynrei, ha ka khyndew baroh la don umjer."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jerubbaal, u Gideon keiñ, bad ki paidbah kiba lem bad u, ki la khie dang step, bad ki la pynïeng dara harud ka pukri Harod: te u paidbah ki Midian u la don shaphang shatei na ki, hajan u lum Moreh, ha ka them.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Trai te u la ong ha u Gideon, “Kine ki briew kiba bad me ki bun eh ïa nga ban ai noh ïa ki Midian ha ka kti jong ki, ba ïoh ki Israel kin sngewsarong ïaleh ïa nga, da kaba ong, ‘Ka kti jong nga hi ka la pynim ïa nga.’",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Namar kata te, to khie pynbna ha ki shkor u paidbah, da ong, ‘Uno uno uba sheptieng bad ba khaw-eit, to un phai bad leit wan noh na u lum Gilead.’ ” Kumta la phai noh na u paidbah arphew ar hajar; bad shiphew hajar ki la sah.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Gideon, “U paidbah u shu dang bun pynban; to ïalam arsut ïa ki sha ka um, te ngan tynjuh ïa ki hangta na ka bynta jong me: bad kan long ruh, ïa uba ngan ong ha me, ‘Une un leit bad me,’ uta keiñ un leit bad me; bad ïa uba ngan ong ha me, ‘Une un ym leit bad me,’ uta un ym ïoh leit.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, u la ïalam arsut ïa u paidbah sha ka um: U Trai te u la ong ha u Gideon, “Uno uno uba jliah um da la u thylliej, kumba u ksew u jliah, ïa uta men buh kyrpang; kumjuh ruh uno uno uba dem la ki khohsiew ban dih.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ka jingkheiñ jong kita kiba jliah da kaba kyndup da ki kti ha la ka shyntur, ka la long laispah ki rangbah: hynrei, kiba sah na u paidbah baroh ki la dem da la ki khohsiew ban dih um.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Gideon, “Da kita ki laispah ki rangbah kiba la jliah ngan pynim ïa phi, bad ngan ai noh ïa ki Midian ha ka kti jong me: bad to ai ba u paidbah baroh uwei pa uwei un leit sha la ka jaka.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, ki briew ki la rah jingbam ha la ki kti, bad ki turoi jong ki: bad u la phah ïa ki paidbah Israel baroh uwei pa uwei sha la ka ïingjaiñ: hynrei, u la bat ïa kita ki laispah ki rangbah: bad ki paidbah ki Midian ki la don harum jong u ha ka them.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ha kata ka miet, U Trai u la ong ha u, “To ïeng joit, to leit hiar sha uta u paidbah; naba nga la ai noh ïa u ha ka kti jong me.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, lada me sheptieng ban leit hiar, to leit hiar ma me lem bad u Purah u shakri jong me sha uta u paidbah:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad men ïohsngew ïa kaei ba ki ïa-ong; bad hadien kata, yn pynkhlaiñ ïa ki kti jong me ïa ka ban leit hiar sha uta u paidbah.” Ynda kumta, u la leit hiar bad u Purah u shakri jong u haduh khap ki nongap phira uta u paidbah.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki Midian te bad ki Amalek bad ki khun mihngi ki la ïathiah ter lter ha ka them ha ka jingkheiñ kum ki puit; bad ki ut jong ki ym lah ñiew shuh, byllien kum u shyiap harud duriaw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ynda u Gideon u la wan, ha khmih, la don u briew uba ïathuh ïa la ka jingphohsniew ha la u lok, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, nga la phohsniew ka jingphohsniew, te kumne, uwei u kpu Barli u tyllun sha u paidïapom Midian, bad u la poi ha kawei ka ïingjaiñ, bad u la pakhuh ïa ka haduh ba ka la ngat, bad u la pynkyllon khongpong ïa ka, ba kata ka ïingjaiñ ka jot noh thiaw.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U lok jong u te u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Kane kam long ei ei, hynrei, tang ka waitlam u Gideon u khun u Joash, u rangbah na Israel: ha ka kti jong u, U Blei u la ai noh ïa ki Midian, bad ïa u paidïapom baroh.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ka la long, haba u Gideon u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingïathuh ïa kata ka jingphohsniew, bad ïa ka jingbatai jong ka, u la mane dem; bad u la leit phai pat sha ka dara jong ki Israel, bad u la ong, “Ïeng; naba U Trai u la ai noh ha ka kti jong phi ïa u paidïapom ki Midian.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la pynïabynta lai kynhun ïa kita ki laispah ki rangbah, bad u la pynbat ki turoi ha ki kti jong ki baroh, bad ki khra suda, bad ki jingtbeh de hapoh kita ki khra.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U la ong ruh ha ki, “To khmih ha nga, bad to leh kumjuh: ha khmih ruh, haba nga poi haduh khap uta u paidbah, te kan long, kumba leh ma nga, kumta to leh ma phi ruh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Haba nga put ka turoi, ma nga bad kiba bad nga, te phi ruh phin put ki turoi baroh sawdong ïa uta u paidbah baroh, bad to ong, ‘Na ka bynta U Trai bad na ka bynta u Gideon.’ ”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumta, u Gideon bad kita ki laispah ki rangbah kiba bad u, ki la wan ha khap uta u paidbah hamar ba sdang ka jingap miet ba hapdeng, haba ki dang ïabujli kata ka jingap: bad ki la put ki turoi, bad ki la pynpait ïa kita ki khra kiba ha ki kti jong ki.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad kita ki lai kynhun ki la put ïa ki turoi, bad ki la pynpait ruh ïa kita ki khra, bad ki la bat ïa kita ki jingtbeh ha ki kti kadiang jong ki, bad ïa ki turoi ha ki kti kamon jong ki ban put da ki: bad ki la pyrta, “Ka waitlam U Trai bad ka jong u Gideon.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki la ïeng te uwei uwei baroh ha la ka jaka baroh sawdong uta u paidbah: te uta u paidïapom baroh u la mareh; bad ki la kynha, bad ki la pynphet ïap ïa ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ki la put ïa kita ki laispah ki turoi, bad U Trai u la pynphai ïa ka waitlam uwei uwei baroh pyrshah ïa la u lok, bad pyrshah ïa u paidïapom baroh: te uta u paidïapom u la phet ïap haduh Beth-shittah shaphang Sererah, haduh ka pud Abel-meholah, hajan Tabbath.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ki rangbah Israel ki la ïalum lang na Naphtali, bad na Asher, bad na Manasseh baroh, bad ki la beh ïa ki Midian.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U Gideon te u la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien ha ka ri lum Ephraim baroh, u da ong, “To ïawan hiar ïaleh ïa ki Midian, bad to ïakhang ha shuwa jong ki, ïa ki um haduh ka Beth-barah, ka Jordan keiñ.” Kumta, ki rangbah Ephraim baroh ki la ïalum lang, bad ki la shim ïa kita ki um haduh Beth-barah, ka Jordan keiñ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ki la kem ïa ki ar ngut ki syiem ki Midian, u Oreb bad u Sib; bad ki la pynïap ïa u Oreb ha u mawsiang Oreb, bad ïa u Sib ki la pynïap ha ka jaka khem umsoh u Sib, bad ki la beh ïa ki Midian: bad ki la wallam ïa ki khlieh jong u Oreb bad u Sib sha u Gideon sha lyndet ka Jordan."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ki rangbah Ephraim te ki la ong ha u, “Balei me la leh kumne ïa ngi, ba mem shym khot ïa ngi haba me la leit ïaleh ïa ki Midian?” Te ki la kren bitar eh ïa u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “Aïu nga la leh te ban ïapyrshang bad ka jong phi? Kaba shu khar ei u soh Waiñ jong u Ephraim kam long kham bha ïa kaba kheit soh u Abieser?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U Blei u la ai noh ha ka kti jong phi ïa ki rangbah ki Midian, ïa u Oreb bad u Sib: te ka leit long aïu kaba nga la leh haba ïapyrshang bad ka jong phi?” Ynda kumta, ka jingbitar jong ki ïa u ka la jem, haba u la lah ong ïa kata.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Gideon te u la wan sha Jordan, bad u la ryngkang sha shiliang, ma u, bad kita ki laispah ngut kiba bad u, kiba la sngewtlot, pynban ki dang ïabeh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U la ong te ha ki rangbah Sukkoth, “Nga kyrpad ïa phi, to ai kpu ïa kine ki paidbah kiba bud ïa nga; naba ki la tlot, bad nga dang beh ïa u Sebah bad u Salmunna, ki syiem ki Midian.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki rangbah Sukkoth ki la ong, “Ki kti jong u Sebah bad u Salmunna ki don mynta ha ka kti jong me, ba ngin leit ai kpu ïa une u paidïapom jong me?”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Gideon u la ong, “Namar kata, ynda U Trai u la ai noh ïa u Sebah bad u Salmunna ha ka kti jong nga, te ngan pynthar ïa ka doh jong phi da ki shiah khlaw bad da ki ñiut shiah.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nangta te u la leit kiew sha Penuel, bad u la kren ha kita kumjuh: bad ki rangbah Penuel ki la jubab ïa u kumjuh kumba la jubab ki rangbah Sukkoth.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u la kren ha ki rangbah Penuel, u da ong, “Ynda nga wan pat ha kaba suk, ngan pyntwa ïa kane ka kut.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Sebah bad u Salmunna ki la don ha Karkor, bad u paidïapom jong ki lem bad ki, kumba khatsan hajar ki rangbah, baroh keiñ kiba dang sah na u paidïapom baroh jong ki khun mihngi: naba la kyllon shispah arphew hajar ki rangbah bakieng atiar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Gideon u la leit kiew na ka lynti jong kita kiba shong ha ki ïingjaiñ sha mihngi ka Nobah bad ka Jogbehah, bad u la pom ïa uta u paidïapom; naba uta u paidïapom u la leh kheiñ kylluid.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Sebah bad u Salmunna ki la phet ïap; te u la beh ïa ki; bad u la kem ïa kita ar ngut ki syiem ki Midian, u Sebah bad u Salmunna bad u la jop khoit ïa uta u paidïapom baroh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Gideon u khun u Joash u la wan phai pat na ka thma na ka thiep Heres.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u la kem ïa uwei u samla na ki nong Sukkoth, bad u la kylli ïa u: u te u la thoh ïa u ki rangbah ka Sukkoth, bad ïa ki basan jong ka, hynñiewphew hynñiew ki rangbah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U la wan te ha ki nong Sukkoth, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, ïa u Sebah bad u Salmunna, shaphang jong kiba phi la krenbeiñ ïa nga, phi da ong, ‘Ki kti u Sebah bad u Salmunna ki don mynta ha ka kti jong me, ba ngin leit ai kpu ha ki briew jong me kiba la thait?’ ”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u la shim ïa ki basan ka shnong, bad ki shiah khlaw bad ki ñiut shiah, bad da kita u la sneng ïa ki rangbah Sukkoth.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ïa ka kut Penuel ruh u la pyntwa, bad u la pynïap ïa ki rangbah ka shnong.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong ha u Sebah bad u Salmunna, “Kiba kumno kita ki briew ïa kiba phi la pynïap ha Tabor?” Ki te ki la ïathuh, “Kumba long ma me, kumta ki la long; ki la long uwei pa uwei kum ki khun syiem.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U la ong te, “Ki la long ki para jong nga, ki khun ka kmie jong nga: katba im U Trai, lada phi la pynim ïa ki, ngan ym pynïap ïa phi.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u la ong ha u Jether, u khun nyngkong jong u, “To ïeng, pynïap ïa ki.” Hynrei, uta u samla um sei ïa la ka waitlam: naba u la sheptieng, namar u la dang khynnah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, u Sebah bad u Salmunna ki la ong, “To ïeng hi ma me, bad to pynïap ïa ngi: naba kumba u rangbah u long, kumta long ka bor jong u.” Kumta, u Gideon u la ïeng joit bad u la pynïap ïa u Sebah bad u Salmunna, bad u la shim ïa ki jingdeng tabit kiba ha ki ryndang ki ut jong ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, ki rangbah Israel ki la ong ha u Gideon, “To synshar ma me halor jong ngi, ma me, bad u khun jong me, bad u khun u khun jong me ruh: naba me la pyllait ïa ngi na ka kti ki Midian.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> U Gideon te u ong ha ki, “Ngan ym synshar halor jong phi, lymne u khun jong nga un ym synshar halor jong phi: U Trai keiñ un synshar halor jong phi.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Gideon u la ong ha ki, “Ngan pan kawei ka jingpan na phi, ba phin ïa-ai ha nga uwei pa uwei ïa ki sohshkor na ka jinglute jong u.” (Naba kita ki la don ki sohshkor ksiar, namar ki la long ki Ishmael.)",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ki te ki la ïathuh, “Ngin ïa-ai sngewbha ïa ki.” Te ki la siang ïa ka jaiñ, bad ki la noh hangta uwei pa uwei ïa ki sohshkor na ka jinglute jong u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad ka jingthew kita ki sohshkor ksiar ba u la pan ka la long shi hajar hynñiewspah shekel ksiar; nalor ki jingdeng tabit, bad ki kpieng, bad ki jaiñ saw bthuh kiba ha kita ki syiem ki Midian, bad nalor ki kynjri kiba ha ryndang ki ut jong ki.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te u Gideon u la shna ka ephod da ki, bad u la buh ïa ka ha la ka shnong, ha Ophrah keiñ: bad ki Israel baroh ki la leit ïaklim ïa ka hangta: kata te, ka la long ka jingriam ïa u Gideon, bad ïa ka ïing jong u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, la jop ïa ki Midian ha khmat ki khun Israel, bad kim shym la pynïeng shuh ïa la ka khlieh. Ka ri te ka la suk sawphew snem ha ki sngi u Gideon.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Jerubbaal u khun u Joash u la leit shong ha la ka jong ka ïing.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad u Gideon u la don hynñiewphew ki khun shynrang kiba la kha na ka met jong u: naba u la don bun ki tnga.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad ka tnga kliar jong u kaba ha Shekhem, ka ruh ka la kha u khun ïa u, bad u la kyrteng “u Abimelekh” ïa u.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u Gideon u khun u Joash u la ïap ba u dap biang ka rta, bad la tep ïa u ha ka jingtep u Joash u kpa jong u, ha Ophrah ki Abieser.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ka la jia te, tang shu ïap u Gideon, ba ki khun Israel ki la phai pat, bad ki la leit ïaklim ïa ki Baal, bad ki la thung blei ha ki da u Baal-berith.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad ki khun Israel kim shym la kynmaw ïa U Trai U Blei jong ki, uba la pyllait ïa ki na ki kti ki nongshun jong ki baroh ha ki phang baroh:",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> lymne kim shym la leh sbun ïa ka ïing u Jerubbaal, u Gideon keiñ, katba kum kata ka jinglehbha baroh kaba u la pyni ha ki Israel."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Abimelekh u khun u Jerubbaal u la leit sha Shekhem sha ki hynmen hynbew ka kmie jong u, bad u la ïakren bad ki, lem bad ki kur ka ïing u kpa ka kmie jong u, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Nga kyrpad ïa phi, to kren ha kaba sngew ki nong Shekhem baroh, ‘La ka kham bha ïa phi, ba ki khun u Jerubbaal baroh, kiba long hynñiewphew ngut ki rangbah, kin synshar halor jong phi, lane ba un synshar uwei halor jong phi?’ To kynmaw ruh ba ma nga, nga long ka shyieng jong phi bad ka doh jong phi.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ki hynmen hynbew ka kmie jong u te ki la kren ïa kine ki ktien baroh shaphang jong u ha kaba sngew ki nong Shekhem baroh: te ki dohnud jong ki, ki la ïadem ban bud ïa u Abimelekh; naba ki la ong, “U long u para jong ngi.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki la ai ha u hynñiewphew ki sbai rupa na ka ïing u Baal-berith; da kita, u Abimelekh u la wer ïa ki briew bathala bad basting, kiba la bud ïa u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la leit sha ïing u kpa jong u ha Ophrah, bad halor uwei u maw u la pynïap ïa la ki hynmen hynbew, ki khun u Jerubbaal keiñ, kiba long hynñiewphew ngut ki rangbah: hynrei, u Jotham u khun khatduh u Jerubbaal u dang sah; naba u la buhrieh ïa lade.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki nong Shekhem baroh ki la ïalang lem bad ka Beth-millo baroh, bad ki la ïaleit bad ki la ïathung syiem ïa u Abimelekh, hajan u dieng Sning mawbynna uba ha Shekhem.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba ki la ïathuh ïa kata ha u Jotham, u la leit bad u la ïeng ha khlieh u lum Gerisim, u la kyang ruh, bad u la pyrta, bad u la ong ha ki, “To sngap ïa nga, phi ki nong Shekhem, ba U Blei un sngap ïa phi ruh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Shi sien ki dieng ki la leit ban thung syiem halor jong ki; bad ki la ong ha u dieng Olib, ‘To synshar ma me halor jong ngi.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, u dieng Olib u la ong ha ki, ‘Hato ngan iehnoh noh mo ïa la ka khleiñ, da kaba da nga ki pyndonburom ïa U Blei bad ïa u briew, bad ban leit kaweh shane shatai halor ki dieng?’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ki dieng te ki la ong ha u dieng Dumbur, ‘Ale ma me, to synshar halor jong ngi.’",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, u dieng Dumbur u la ong ha ki, ‘Hato ngan iehnoh noh mo ïa la ka jingthiang, bad la u soh babha, bad ban leit kaweh shane shatai halor ki dieng?’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, ki dieng ki la ong ha u dieng soh Waiñ, ‘Ale ma me, to synshar halor jong ngi.’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U dieng soh Waiñ te u la ong ha ki, ‘Hato ngan iehnoh noh mo ïa la ka Waiñ, kaba pynsngewbha ïa U Blei bad ïa u briew, bad ban leit kaweh shane shatai halor ki dieng?’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ki dieng baroh ki la ong ha u dieng shiah, ‘Ale ma me, to synshar halor jong ngi.’",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U dieng shiah te u la ong ha ki dieng, ‘Lada da shisha phin thung syiem ïa nga halor jong phi, ale te to shaniah ha ka syrngiew jong nga: lymda kumta, ai kan mih ka ding na u dieng shiah, bad kan bam duh ïa ki Kedar u Lebanon.’",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Namar kata te, lada phi la leh kaba shisha bad ka bahok, ha kaba phi la thung syiem ïa u Abimelekh, bad lada phi la leh kaba dei bad u Jerubbaal bad ka ïing jong u, bad lada phi la leh ïa u katba kum ka jingdawa ki kam ki kti jong u;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> (naba u kpa jong nga u la ïaleh thma na ka bynta jong phi, bad u la kheiñduh ïa la ka jingim, bad u la pyllait ïa phi na ka kti ki Midian:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> phi te phi la ïeng ïaleh ïa ka ïing u kpa jong nga ha kane ka sngi, bad phi la pynïap halor uwei u maw, ïa ki khun shynrang jong u hynñiewphew ngut ki rangbah, bad phi la pynlong syiem halor ki nong Shekhem ïa u Abimelekh, u khun ka shakri jong u, namar ba u long u para jong phi;)",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> lada phi te phi la leh kaba shisha bad kaba dei bad u Jerubbaal bad ka ïing jong u ruh ha kane ka sngi, kumta te, to leh kmen ha u Abimelekh, bad to u ruh un leh kmen ha phi:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hynrei, lada ym kumta, ai kan mih ka ding na u Abimelekh, bad kan bam duh ïa ki nong Shekhem, bad ïa ka ïing Millo; bad ai kan mih ka ding na ki nong Shekhem, bad na ka ïing Millo, bad kan bam duh ïa u Abimelekh.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jotham u la mareh, bad u la phet ïap noh, bad u la leit sha Beer, bad u la shong hangta, namar kaba sheptieng ïa u Abimelekh u hynmen jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Abimelekh u la long rangbah halor ki Israel lai snem.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te U Blei u la phah ka mynsiem bymman hapdeng u Abimelekh bad ki nong Shekhem; bad ki nong Shekhem ki la ïasiar kylla ïa u Abimelekh:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> khnang ba ka jingleh runar ïa ki hynñiewphew ngut ki khun u Jerubbaal kan ïoh wan, bad ba yn tei ïa ka snam jong ki halor u Abimelekh u para jong ki, uba la pynïap ïa ki, bad halor ki nong Shekhem, kiba la ai bor ïa ki kti jong u ban pynïap ïa la ki para.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ki nong Shekhem ki la buh ïa ki nongsyntiat ïa u ha kliar ki lum, bad ki la lute ïa kat kiba wan na kata ka lynti hajan jong ki: bad la ïathuh ïa kata ha u Abimelekh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u Gaal u khun u Ebed u la wan lem bad ki para jong u, bad u la leit ha Shekhem: ki nong Shekhem te ki la shaniah ha u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ki la leit te sha ki lyngkha, bad ki la ïakheit soh Waiñ, bad ki la khñiot ïa ki soh, bad ki la pynlong ka jingkhawai, ki la leit ruh sha ïing u blei jong ki, bad ki la bam ki la dih, bad ki la tim ïa u Abimelekh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u Gaal u khun u Ebed u la ong, “Uei u Abimelekh, bad uei u Shekhem, ba ngin shakri ïa u? um long ma u, u khun u Jerubbaal? bad u Sebul, u myntri jong u? to shakri phi ïa ki rangbah u Hamor u kpa u Shekhem: hynrei, balei ngin leit shakri ma ngi ïa uta?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> A ban da long une u paidbah ha ka kti jong nga! te ngan pynkynriah ïa u Abimelekh. Te u la ong ha u Abimelekh, ‘To pynkhraw ïa la u paidïapom, bad to wan mih noh.’ ”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te haba u Sebul u nongsynshar ka shnong u la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien u Gaal u khun u Ebed, ka jingbitar jong u ka la meh lep.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien ha u Abimelekh ha kaba rieh, u da ong, “Ha khmih, u Gaal u khun u Ebed bad la ki para ki la wan sha Shekhem; bad ha khmih, ki pynbor ïa ka shnong ban ïaleh ïa me.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te namar kata, to khie mynmiet, ma me bad ki paid kiba bad me, bad to ap syntiat ha madan:",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> te mynstep, tang shu mih ka sngi, men ïeng dang step, ban ïaleh ïa ka shnong; te ha khmih, haba ma u bad ki briew kiba bad u kin mih ïaleh ïa me, ynda kumta, men ïaleh ïa ki katba me shem lad.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kumta, u Abimelekh u la ïeng joit, bad ki briew baroh kiba bad u, mynmiet, bad ki la ap thap ïaleh ïa ka Shekhem saw kynhun.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad u Gaal u khun u Ebed u la mih noh shabar, bad u la ïeng ha khmat ka khyrdop jong ka shnong: u Abimelekh te u la ïeng joit bad kita ki paidbah kiba bad u na kaba ap thap.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te haba u Gaal u la ïohi ïa kita ki paidbah, u la ong ha u Sebul, “Ha khmih, don ki briew kiba wan hiar na kliar lum.” Te u Sebul u la ong ha u, “Ïa ka syrngiew ki lum me i kum ki briew.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te u Gaal u la nang kren, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, don ki briew kiba wan hiar napdeng ka ri, bad shi kynhun ki wan na ka lynti u dieng Sning Meonenim.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ynda kumta, u Sebul u la ong ha u, “Shano mynta ka shyntur jong me, ba me la ong, ‘Uei uta u Abimelekh, ba ngin leit shakri ïa u?’ Une u long u paidbah ïa uba me la ibeiñ: to leit mih noh mynta, nga kyrpad, bad to ïaleh bad ki.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad u Gaal u la leit mih noh ha phrang ki rangbah Shekhem, bad u la ïaleh bad u Abimelekh.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> U Abimelekh te u la beh ïa u, bad u la phet na khmat jong u, bun ruh ki la kyllon ba la mynsaw, wat haduh khmat ka khyrdop.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te u Abimelekh u la shong ha Arumah: bad u Sebul u la beh noh ïa u Gaal bad ki hynmen hynbew jong u, ba kin ym shong shuh ha Shekhem.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te kum lashai, ki briew ki la mih noh sha madan; bad ki la ïathuh ha u Abimelekh.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> U te u la shim ïa ki paidbah, bad u la ïabynta lai kynhun ïa ki, bad ki la ïa-ap thap ha lyngkha; bad u la khmih, te ha khmih, ki briew ki la ïamih na shnong; bad u la ïeng ïaleh ïa ki, bad u la jop ïa ki.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te u Abimelekh, bad kita ki kynhun kiba la don bad u, ki la tur pyrshah, bad u la ïeng ha khmat khyrdop ka shnong bad kita ki ar kynhun ki la tur sha kita baroh kiba ha madan, bad ki la jop ïa ki.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Bad u Abimelekh u la ïaleh thma ïa kata ka shnong baroh shi sngi; bad u la jop ïa ka shnong, bad u la pynïap ïa ki rangbah ba don ha ka: bad u la pynduh ïa ka shnong, bad u la ber ïa ka da ka mluh.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Te haba ki rangbah ka kut Shekhem baroh ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la rung shapoh ka kut jong ka ïing u El-berith.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bad la ïathuh ïa u Abimelekh ba ki rangbah ka kut Shekhem baroh ki la lum lang.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> U Abimelekh te u la leit kiew sha u lum Salmon, ma u bad ki paidbah kiba bad u baroh: bad u Abimelekh u la shim ka wait ha la ka kti, bad u la pom ka tnat dieng, bad u la shim ïa ka, u la buh ruh ha la ka tyrpeng: bad u la ong ha ki paidbah kiba la don bad u, “Ïa kaba phi la ïohi ba nga la leh, to pynkloi bad leh ruh kumba la leh ma nga.”",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Bad kita ki paidbah baroh kumjuh ki la pom uwei uwei la ka tnat, bad ki la bud ïa u Abimelekh, bad ki la buh ïa ki ha kata ka kut, bad ki la thang ïa kata ka kut halor jong ki; kumta, ki briew jong ka kut Shekhem baroh ki la ïap, kumba shi hajar ki shynrang bad ki kynthei.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abimelekh u la leit sha Thebes, bad u la sher dara ïaleh ïa ka Thebes bad u la jop ïa ka.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Hynrei, la don hapoh kata ka shnong ka kut baskhem, bad hangta ki la phet ki shynrang bad ki kynthei baroh, bad kiba na ka shnong baroh, bad ki la khang ïa lade shapoh, bad ki la kiew shalor kata ka kut.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> U Abimelekh u la wan te sha kata ka kut, bad u la ïaleh ïa ka, bad u la leit hajan ka jingkhang jong kata ka kut ban thang ïa ka da ka ding.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Te kawei ka kynthei ka la lynthem da u mawtylliat uba nalor ha ka khlieh u Abimelekh, bad ka la pynpait ïa ka shynrong jong u.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Te u la khot kyrkieh ïa uta u samla uba rah ïa ki atiar jong u, bad u la ong ïa u, “To sei ïa ka waitlam, to pynïap ïa nga, ba ki briew kin ym ong shaphang jong nga, ‘Ka kynthei ka la pynïap ïa u.’ ” Te uta u samla jong u, u la dung lyngba ïa u, bad u la ïap.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Te haba ki rangbah Israel ki la ïohi ba la ïap u Abimelekh, ki la leit noh uwei uwei sha la ka jaka.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Kumne U Blei u la pynhiar kput ïa ka jingbymman u Abimelekh, kaba u la leh ïa la u kpa, ha kaba u pynïap ïa ki hynñiewphew ngut ki hynmen hynbew jong u:",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> bad baroh ka jingbymman ki rangbah Shekhem U Blei u la pynhiar kput halor ki khlieh jong ki: bad ka jingtim u Jotham u khun u Jerubbaal ka la wanhap halor jong ki."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hadien u Abimelekh la mih ban ïada ïa ki Israel u Tola u khun u Puah, u khun u Dodo, u briew na ka jaid Issakhar; te u shong ha Shamir ha ri lum Ephraim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la bishar ïa ki Israel arphew lai snem, te u la ïap, bad ki la tep ïa u ha Shamir.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hadien jong u te la mih u Jair, u nong Gilead, bad u la bishar ïa ki Israel arphew ar snem.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la don laiphew ngut ki khun shynrang kiba shong halor laiphew tylli ki khun kadda, bad ki la don laiphew tylli ki shnong, ïa kiba la khot “Habboth-jair” haduh kane ka sngi, kiba don ha ri Gilead.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Jair u la ïap, bad la tep ïa u ha Kamon.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la leh pat ïa kata ka basniew ha khmat U Trai, bad ki la leit shakri ïa ki Baal bad ki Ashtaroth, bad ïa ki blei ka Syria, bad ïa ki blei ka Sidon, bad ïa ki blei ki Moab, bad ïa ki blei ki khun u Ammon, bad ïa ki blei ki Philistia; te ki la lyndet ïa U Trai, bad kim shakri shuh ïa u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ka jingbitar U Trai ka la meh lep ïa ki Israel, bad u la die ïa ki ha ka kti ki Philistia, bad ha ka kti ki khun u Ammon.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ki te ki la pynjynjar bad ki la ban shitom ïa ki khun Israel ha kata ka snem: khatphra snem ki la ban shitom ïa ki khun Israel baroh kiba sha shiliang ka Jordan ha ka ri ki Amor, kaba ha Gilead.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki khun u Ammon ki la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan ban ïaleh ïa u Judah ruh, bad ïa u Benjamin, bad ïa ka ïing u Ephraim de; kumta, ki Israel ki la jynjar eh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la lynñiar ha U Trai, ki la ong, “Ngi la leh pop ïa me, namar ba ngi la lyndet ïa U Blei jong ngi, bad ngi la leit shakri ïa ki Baal.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ïa ki khun Israel, “Nga ngam shym la pyllait ïa phi na ki nong Ijipt, bad na ki Amor, na ki khun u Ammon, bad na ki Philistia?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki Sidon ruh, bad ki Amalek, bad ki Maon, ki la banbeiñ ïa phi; te phi la lynñiar ha nga bad nga la pyllait ïa phi na ka kti jong ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Pynban, phi la lyndet ïa nga, bad phi la leit shakri ïa kiwei pat ki blei: namar kata, ngan ym pyllait shuh ïa phi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Khie leit kyrpad ïa kita ki blei kiba phi la jied; to kita keiñ kin pyllait ïa phi ha ka por ka jingjynjar jong phi.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ki khun Israel te ki la ong ha U Trai, “Ngi la leh pop: to leh ïa ngi ïa kaei kaei ruh katba me ibit; ngi duwai ïa me, tang ba men pyllait ïa ngi ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki la bred noh ïa ki blei khyllah napdeng jong ki, bad ki la shakri ïa U Trai: te ka mynsiem jong u ka la sngewsih na ka bynta ka jingjynjar ki Israel.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, ki khun u Ammon ki la ïalang, bad ki la sher dara ha Gilead. Bad ki khun Israel de ki la ïalang, bad ki la sher dara ha Mispeh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u paidbah ki rangbah Gilead, ki la ïa-ong paralok hi, “Uei uta u briew u ban sdang ïaleh thma ïa ki khun u Ammon? uta un long u rangbah halor ki nong Gilead baroh.”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Jephthah u khun u nong Gilead u la long u briew bakhlaiñ bad bashlur, bad u la long u khun ka nuti: bad u Gilead u la pynkha ïa u Jephthah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ka tnga u Gilead ka la kha ki khun shynrang ïa u; bad ynda kita ki khun ka tnga jong u ki la san, ki la beh noh ïa u Jephthah, bad ki la ong ha u, “Men ym ïoh bynta ha ka ïing u kpa jong ngi; naba me long u khun kawei pat ka briew.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kumta te u Jephthah u la phet noh na khmat ki hynmen hynbew jong u, bad u la shong ha ka ri Tob: te ki la ïalang ki 'riewthala ha u Jephthah, bad ki la ïaleit mih noh lem bad u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ynda katto katne, ki khun u Ammon ki la pynlong thma bad ki Israel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba ki khun u Ammon ki la pynlong thma ïa ki Israel, ki rangbah Gilead ki la leit shaw ïa u Jephthah na ka ri Tob:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad ki la ong ha u Jephthah, “To ale, bad to long u rangbah jong ngi, ba ngin leit ïaleh thma ïa ki khun u Ammon.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Jephthah u la ong ha ki rangbah Gilead, “Phim shym la isih ïa nga, bad phi la beh ïa nga na ka ïing u kpa jong nga? balei te phi wan ha nga mynta haba phi la shipa?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ki rangbah Gilead te ki la ong ïa u Jephthah, “Namar kata, ngi wan phai pat sha me mynta, ba men leit lem bad ngi, bad ïaleh ïa ki khun u Ammon, bad men long ruh u rangbah jong ngi halor ki nong Gilead baroh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Jephthah u la ong ïa ki rangbah jong ka Gilead, “Lada phin wallam pat ïa nga sha la ïing ban ïaleh ïa ki khun u Ammon, bad ba U Trai un aiti noh ïa ki ha khmat jong nga, ngan ïoh long u rangbah jong phi?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki rangbah jong ka Gilead ki la ong ïa u Jephthah, “U Trai un long u sakhi hapdeng jong ngi; shisha katba kum ka ktien jong me kumta keiñ ngin leh.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jephthah u la leit ryngkat bad ki rangbah jong ka Gilead, bad u paidbah u la pynlong ïa u, u rangbah bad u nongïalam halor jong ki: te u Jephthah u la kren ïa ki ktien jong u baroh ha khmat U Trai ha Mispeh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Jephthah u la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien sha u syiem ki khun u Ammon, u da ong, “Me donkam aïu bad nga, ba me la wan ha nga ban ïaleh thma ïa ka ri jong nga?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U syiem ki khun u Ammon te u la phai ktien ha ki nonglam-ktien u Jephthah, “Namar ba ki Israel ki la knieh noh ïa ka khyndew jong nga mynba ki la wan kiew na ka ri Ijipt, naduh Arnon haduh Jabbok keiñ, bad haduh Jordan: mynta te, to ai noh pat ïa kito ki khyndew ha kaba suk.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Jephthah u la phah pat ïa ki nonglam-ktien ha u syiem ki khun u Ammon:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad u la ong ha u, “Kumne u ong u Jephthah: Ki Israel kim shym la knieh noh ïa ka ri Moab, lymne ïa ka ri ki khun u Ammon:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> hynrei, mynba ki la wan kiew na ka ri Ijipt, bad ki Israel ki la ïaid lyngba ka ri khlaw haduh ka Duriaw Basaw, bad ki la wan sha Kadesh;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ynda kumta, ki Israel ki la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien sha u syiem ka Edom, ki da ong, ‘To shah ïa nga, nga kyrpad ïa me, ban ïaid lyngba ka ri jong me:’ hynrei, u syiem ka Edom um sngap. Kumjuh ruh ki la phah sha u syiem ka Moab: u ruh um shah; kumta, ki Israel ki la shong ha Kadesh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïaid lyngba kata ka ri khlaw, da kaba ïaid tawiar ïa ka ri Edom, bad ïa ka ri Moab, bad ki la wan na shaphang mihngi ka ri Moab bad ki la sher dara sha shiliang jong ka Arnon; hynrei, kim shym la jam sha ka pud Moab, naba ka Arnon ka la long ka pud Moab.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki Israel ki la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien sha u Sihon u syiem ki Amor, u syiem ka Heshbon keiñ; bad ki Israel ki la ong ha u, ‘To shah ïa ngi, ngi kyrpad ïa me, ban ïaid lyngba ka ri jong me sha ka jaka jong nga.’",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, u Sihon um shaniah ïa ki Israel ban ïaid lyngba ka pud jong u: hynrei, u Sihon u la ïalum lang ïa la ki briew baroh, bad u la sher dara ha Jahas, bad u la ïaleh thma ïa ki Israel.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, u la ai noh ïa u Sihon bad ki briew jong u baroh ha ka kti ki Israel, bad ki la jop ïa ki: kumta, ki Israel ki la ïoh kynti ïa ka ri ki Amor baroh, kiba long ki trai-shnong kata ka ri.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki la ïoh ruh ki phang ka ri ki Amor baroh, naduh ka Arnon haduh ka Jabbok keiñ, bad naduh ka ri khlaw haduh ka Jordan.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta te U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, u la pynduh ïa ki Amor na khmat ki Israel u paidbah jong u, me pynban men ïoh ïa kita?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Men ym ïoh ïa kata kaba u Khemosh, u blei jong me, u ai ïa me ban ïoh? Kumta ïano ïano ba U Trai U Blei jong ngi u la pynduh ha khmat jong ngi, ïa kita ngin ïoh keiñ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te mynta me long kham bha kumno kumno ïa u Balak u khun u Sippor, u syiem ka Moab? hato u la ju ïa-pyneh bad ki Israel, lane u la ju ïaleh thma ïa ki?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Katba ki Israel ki la shong ha Heshbon bad ki shnong jong ka, bad ha Aroer bad ki shnong jong ka, bad ha ki nongbah baroh kiba harud ka Arnon, laispah snem; hato balei te phim shym la pynïoh ïa ki ha kata ka por?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar kata, nga ngam shym la leh pop ïa me, hynrei, me seh me leh bymdei ïa nga ban ïaleh thma ïa nga: to U Trai, uta u Nongbishar, un long nongbishar ha kane ka sngi hapdeng ki khun Israel bad ki khun u Ammon.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> La kumta ruh, u syiem ki khun u Ammon um sngap ïa ki ktien u Jephthah kiba u la phah ha u.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Hamar kata, U Mynsiem U Trai u la wan ha u Jephthah, bad u la ïaid lyngba ïa ka Gilead bad ïa ka Manasseh, bad u la ïaid lyngba ïa ka Mispeh jong ka Gilead, bad na ka Mispeh jong ka Gilead u la ïaid sha shiliang sha ki khun u Ammon.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u Jephthah u la kular ïa ka kular ha U Trai, bad u la ong, “Lada men ai noh da shisha ïa ki khun u Ammon ha ka kti jong nga,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> te kan long, ba kano kano ba-mih noh na ki jingkhang ka ïing jong nga ban tan ïa nga, haba nga wan phai pat ha kaba suk na ki khun u Ammon, kan long ka jong U Trai, bad ngan ainguh ïa ka kum ka jingainguh thang.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kumta, u Jephthah u la leit sha shiliang sha ki khun u Ammon ban ïaleh thma ïa ki: te U Trai u la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u la jop ïa ki naduh ka Arnon haduh kaba poi sha Minnith, arphew tylli ki shnong keiñ, bad haduh Abel-keramin, da ka jingpynïap bajur eh. Kumta, la jop ïa ki khun u Ammon ha khmat ki khun Israel.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u Jephthah u la wan poi sha Mispeh sha la ïing, te, ha khmih, ka khun jong u ka la wan mih ban tan ïa u, bad ki kanjari bad ki jingshad de: ka la long ruh ka khun marwei jong u, nalor jong ka, um shym la don khun shynrang ne kynthei.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te haba u la ïohi ïa ka; u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad u la ong, “Waw, ko khun! pha la pyndiaw eh ïa nga, bad pha long kawei na kita ba pynjynjar ïa nga: naba nga la ang ïa la ka shyntur ha U Trai, bad ngam lah kynran shuh.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ka te ka la ong ïa u, “Ko pa, me la ang ïa la ka shyntur ha U Trai; to leh ïa nga katba kum kata ba la mih noh na ka shyntur jong me; namar ba U Trai u la pynhiar kput na ka bynta jong me ha ki nongshun jong me, ha ki khun u Ammon keiñ.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ka la ong te ha la u kpa, “To leh ïa kane na ka bynta jong nga; to shah ïa nga ar bnai, ba ngan ïaid arsut artet shalor ki lum, bad ban ïam ïa ka jinglong sotti jong nga, ma nga bad ki lok jong nga.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te u la ong ïa ka, “To leit.” Bad u la phah noh ïa ka, ar bnai: ka te ka la leit, ma ka bad ki lok jong ka, bad ki la ïaïam na ka bynta ka jinglong sotti jong ka halor ki lum.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te haba la kut kita ar bnai, ka la wan phai pat sha la u kpa, uba la leh ïa ka kat kum ka kular jong u kaba u la lah smai: te kam shym la ithuh ïa u briew.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad ka la long ka rukom ha Israel, ba ki khun kynthei Israel ki la ju leit man la ka snem ban ïaroh ïa ka khun u Jephthah u nong Gilead saw sngi shi snem."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki rangbah Ephraim ki la ïalum lang, bad ki la ïaid shaphang shatei; bad ki la ong ïa u Jephthah, “Namar balei me la leit ïaleh thma ïa ki khun u Ammon, bad mem shym la khot ïa ngi ban leit lem bad me? Ngin thang ïa ka ïing jong me, halor jong me da ka ding.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Jephthah te u la ong ha ki, “Nga bad ki briew jong nga ngi la ïaleh jur eh bad ki khun u Ammon; bad haba nga la khot ïa phi, phim shym la pyllait ïa nga na ka kti jong ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba nga la ïohi ba phim shym la pyllait ïa nga, nga la kheiñduh ïa la ka mynsiem, bad nga la leit sha shiliang pyrshah ïa ki khun u Ammon, bad U Trai u la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong nga: te namar balei ba phi la wan ha nga ha kane ka sngi, ban ïaleh thma ïa nga?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jephthah u la ïalum lang ïa ki rangbah Gilead baroh, bad u la ïaleh thma ïa ki Ephraim: bad ki rangbah Gilead ki la jop ïa ki Ephraim, namar ba ki la ong, “Phi ki nong Gilead, phi long ki nongphetwir jong ki Ephraim hapdeng ki Ephraim bad hapdeng ki Manasseh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ki nong Gilead ki la ïoh ïa ki khriang ka Jordan ha shuwa ki Ephraim: te ka la long, haba uno uno na ki nongphet thma jong ki Ephraim u ong, “Shah ba ngan leit sha shiliang,” ki nong Gilead ki la ong ha u, “Me long u Ephraim?” Lada u ong, “Em;”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> te ki la ong ïa u, “Te to ong Shibboleth;” bad u la ong “Sibboleth;” naba um lait ban kynnoh beit ïa ka; ynda kumta, ki la kem ïa u, bad ki la pynïap ïa u ha ki khriang ka Jordan: la kyllon te ha kata ka por na ki Ephraim sawphew ar hajar.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Jephthah u la bishar ïa ki Israel hynriew snem. Ynda kumta, u Jephthah u nong Gilead u la ïap, bad la tep ïa u ha kawei na ki shnong Gilead.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hadien jong u te u Ibsan na Bethlehem u la bishar ïa ki Israel.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u la don laiphew ngut ki khun shynrang, bad ïa ki laiphew ngut ki khun kynthei u la phah na la ïing, bad ïa laiphew ngut ki khun kynthei u la wallam sha la ïing nawei nawei ïa ki khun shynrang jong u. Bad u la bishar ïa ki Israel hynñiew snem.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Ibsan u la ïap, bad la tep ïa u ha Bethlehem.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hadien jong u te u Elon u nong Sabulon u la bishar ïa ki Israel; bad u la bishar ïa ki Israel shiphew snem.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Elon u nong Sabulon u la ïap, bad la tep ïa u ha Aijalon ha ka ri Sabulon.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad hadien jong u, u Abdon u khun u Hillel u nong Pirathon u la bishar ïa ki Israel.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U la don te sawphew ngut ki khun shynrang bad laiphew ngut ki ksiew, kiba shong halor ki hynñiewphew tylli ki khun kadda: bad u la bishar ïa ki Israel phra snem.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> U Abdon u khun u Hillel u nong Pirathon u la ïap, bad la tep ïa u ha Pirathon ha ka ri ki Ephraim, ha ri lum jong ki Amalek."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la nang leh ïa kata ka basniew pat ha khmat U Trai; bad U Trai u la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti ki Philistia sawphew snem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> La don te uwei u briew ha Sorah, na ka jaid Dan, uba kyrteng “u Manoah”; bad ka tnga jong u ka la long kaba lyngki, ka bym shym kha.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U angel U Trai te u la paw ha kata ka kynthei, bad u la ong ha ka, “Ha khmih te, pha kaba lyngki, bad ka bymkha: hynrei, phan sa punkhun, phan kha ruh ïa u khun shynrang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Namar kata te, to sumar, nga kyrpad ïa pha, wat dih Waiñ lymne kyiad, bad wat bam kaei kaei ka bymkhuid:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> naba ha khmih, phan sa punkhun, bad phan kha khun shynrang; ka syrti kan ym dei ïa ka khlieh jong u: naba uta u khunlung un long u Nasar ha U Blei naduh ka kpoh: bad un sdang ban pyllait ïa ki Israel na ka kti ki Philistia.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te kata ka kynthei ka la wan ïathuh ha u tnga jong ka, ka da ong, “U briew jong U Blei u la wan ha nga, bad ka khmat jong u ka la long kum ka khmat u angel U Blei, kaba iphieng eh; hynrei, ngam shym kylli ïa u nangno u la long, lymne um shym ïathuh ïa nga ïa la ka kyrteng:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> hynrei, u la ong ha nga, ‘Ha khmih, phan sa punkhun, phan kha ruh u khun; mynta te wat dih Waiñ lymne kyiad, lymne wat bam kaei kaei ka bymkhuid: naba uta u khynnah un long u Nasar ha U Blei naduh ka kpoh haduh ka sngi ka jingïap jong u.’ ”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, u Manoah u la kyrpad ïa U Trai, bad u la ong, “A Trai, nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ba uta u briew jong U Blei ïa uba me la phah un wan pat ha ngi, ban bthah ïa ngi kumno ngin leh ïa uta u khunlung u ban sa kha.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Blei te u la shahshkor ïa ka jingkyrpad u Manoah; bad u angel U Blei u la wan pat ha kata ka briew katba ka dang shong ha lyngkha: hynrei, u Manoah u tnga jong ka um shym la don lem bad ka.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ka kynthei ka la pynkloi, bad ka la mareh ruh, bad ka la ïathuh ïa la u tnga, ka la ong ruh ha u, “Ha khmih, uta u briew u la paw ha nga, uta uba la wan ha nga ha kata ka sngi.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Manoah te u la ïeng, bad u la bud ïa la ka tnga, bad haba u la wan ha uta u briew, u la ong ha u, “Me long uta u briew uba la kren ha kane ka kynthei?” U te u la ong, “Nga long.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Manoah u la ong te, “Mynta ai ba yn pyndep ïa ki ktien jong me: kaba kumno ka jinglong uta u khynnah, bad kaei kan long ka kam jong u?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u angel U Trai u la ong ha u Manoah, “Ïa kita baroh ba nga la ong ha ka kynthei, to kan sumar.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kam dei ïa ka ban bam ei ei kaba mih noh na u dieng Waiñ, lymne kan ym dih Waiñ ne kyiad, lymne bam kaei kaei ka bymkhuid; ïa baroh ba nga la hukum ïa ka to kan sumar.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Manoah u la ong ha u angel U Trai, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, shah ba ngin bat ïa me, ba ngin pynkhreh ïa u khun blang ïa me.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u angel U Trai u la ong ha u Manoah, “La me bat ïa nga, ngan ym bam na u kpu jong me: te lada men pynkhreh ïa ka jingainguh thang ruh, ka dei ba men ainguh ïa ka ha U Trai.” Naba u Manoah um tip ba u la long u angel U Trai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Manoah u la ong ha u angel U Trai, “Kaei ka kyrteng jong me, ba haba ki ktien jong me kin wan jia ngin ïoh lehburom ïa me?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u angel U Trai u la ong ha u, “Balei me kylli ïa ka kyrteng jong nga, namar ka long kaba phylla?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kumta, u Manoah u la shim ïa uta u khun blang lem bad ka jingainguh bam, bad u la ainguh ïa ka halor u mawsiang ha U Trai: te u angel u la leh phylla, bad u Manoah bad ka tnga jong u de ki la ïakhmih.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Naba haba ka thylliej ding ka la kiew sha bneng na ka duwan, u angel U Trai u la kiew ha kata ka thylliej ding jong ka duwan: u Manoah te bad ka tnga jong u ki la ïakhmih; bad ki la dem la ki khmat haduh khyndew.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, uta u angel U Trai um shym paw shuh ha u Manoah lane ha ka tnga jong u. Ynda kumta, u Manoah u la tip ba u la long u angel U Trai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Manoah u la ong ha la ka tnga, “Ngin ïap shisha, namar ngi la ïohi ïa U Blei.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, ka tnga jong u ka la ong ha u, “Lada U Trai u la mon ban pynïap ïa ngi, un ym da pdiang ïa ka jingainguh thang bad ka jingainguh bam na ka kti jong ngi, lymne un ym da pyni ha ngi ïa kine kiei kiei baroh, lymne ha kane ka por un ym da ïathuh ïa kiei kiei kat kine.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kata ka kynthei te ka la kha khun shynrang, bad la kyrteng ïa u, “u Samson”: bad uta u khynnah u la nang san, bad U Trai u la kyrkhu ïa u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad U Mynsiem U Trai u la sdang ban pynskuiñ ïa u ha Mahaneh-dan, hapdeng ka Sorah bad ka Eshtaol."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Samson u la leit hiar sha Timnath, bad u la ïohi ïa ka briew ha Timnath na ki khun kynthei ki Philistia.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te haba u la wan noh, u la ïathuh ha la u kpa bad ha la ka kmie, bad u la ong, “Nga la ïohi ïa kawei ka briew ha Timnath na ki khun kynthei jong ki Philistia: mynta te, to shim ïa ka ban long ka tnga jong nga.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U kpa bad ka kmie jong u te ki la ong ha u, “Hato ym don kynthei hapdeng ki khun kynthei ki para jong me, lane hapdeng ki briew jong nga baroh, ba men shu leit ïoh tnga na ki Philistia kiba khlem otsher?” Te u Samson u la ong ha la u kpa, “Pynïoh ïa ka ha nga; naba nga ibha eh ïa ka.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, u kpa bad ka kmie jong u kim shym tip ba kane ka la long na U Trai; naba u la wad ka lad ban ïaleh ïa ki Philistia. Te ha kata ka por, ki Philistia ki la synshar halor ki Israel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, u Samson u la leit hiar, bad u kpa bad ka kmie jong u, sha Timnath: bad u la wan sha ki brisoh Waiñ ka Timnath: te, ha khmih, u sing khynraw u la kyrhuh pyrshah ïa u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te U Mynsiem U Trai u la wan borbah halor jong u, bad u la kad ïa u kumba kad ïa i khun blang, te um shym don ei ei ha ka kti jong u: hynrei, um shym la ïathuh ïa u kpa lane ïa ka kmie ïa kaba u la leh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U la leit hiar te, bad u la kren bad kata ka briew; bad u Samson u la ibha eh ïa ka.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sa katto katne u la leit phai pat ban shim ïa ka, bad u la leit artad ban khmih ïa ka metïap uta u sing: te, ha khmih, shi kiaw u ngap la don hapoh ka met uta u sing, bad ka ngap de.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U te u la shim ïa ka ha la ki kti, bad u la nang leit, u da bam ïaïaid, te haba u la lap ïa la u kpa bad ka kmie, u la ai ha ki, ki ruh ki la bam: hynrei, um shym la ïathuh ha ki ba u la khlaw ïa kata ka ngap na ka metïap uta u sing.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u kpa jong u, u la leit hiar sha kata ka briew: bad u Samson u la thaw ka jingkhawai hangta; naba kumta ki samla ki ju leh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba ki la ïohi ïa u, ki la wallam laiphew ngut ki lok ban long lem bad u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Samson u la ong ïa ki, “To shah ngan pyni mynta ha phi ïa kawei ka jingkyntip: lada phi lah ban ïathuh ïa ka ha nga hapdeng ki hynñiew sngi jong ka jingkhawai, bad phin tip ïa ka, te ngan ai ha phi laiphew tylli ki jaiñ linen bad laiphew kup laiphew sem:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> hynrei, lada phim lah ban ïathuh ïa ka ha nga, phi te phin ai ha nga laiphew ki jaiñ linen bad laiphew kup laiphew sem.” Te ki la ong ïa u, “Sei ïa ka jingkyntip jong me, ba ngin ïohsngew ïa ka.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u la ong ha ki, “Na u nongbam la mih ka jingbam, bad na uba khlaiñ la mih ka jingthiang.” Bad lai sngi kim lah ban ïathuh ïa kata ka jingkyntip.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew, ki la ong ha ka tnga u Samson, “To ïapah ïa la u tnga ba un ïathuh ïa ngi ïa kata ka jingkyntip, ïoh ngin thang ïa pha bad ïa ka ïing u kpa jong pha da ka ding: hato phi la khot ïa ngi ban pynduh ïa ngi? Ym long kumta mo?”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ka tnga u Samson ka la ïam ha khmat jong u, bad ka la ong, “Pleng me uba shun ïa nga, bad mem ieit satia ïa nga: me la sei ïa ka jingkyntip ha ki khun ki briew jong nga, bad mem shym pyntip ïa ka ha nga.” U te u la ong ha ka, “Ha khmih, ngam shym pyntip ïa ka ha la u kpa lymne ka kmie, te ngan pyntip ha pha?”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ka la ïam ha khmat jong u ha kita ki hynñiew sngi, katba dang sah ka jingkhawai jong ki: bad ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew, u la pyntip ïa ka, namar ka la ïaipynsatia eh ïa u: ka te ka la pyntip ïa kata ka jingkyntip ha ki khun ki briew jong ka.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki briew jong kata ka shnong ki la ong ha u ha ka sngi ka bahynñiew haba ym pat sep ka sngi, “Kaei kaba kham thiang ban ïa ka ngap? bad uei uba kham khlaiñ ban ïa u sing?” U la ong te ha ki, “Lada phim shym la lur da ka masi jong nga, phim shym la shem ïa ka jingkyntip jong nga.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te U Mynsiem U Trai u la wan borbah halor jong u, bad u la leit hiar sha Ashkelon, te haba u la pynïap laiphew ngut na ki, u la shim ïa ki jaiñ jong ki, bad u la ai ïa kita ki jaiñ ha kita kiba la tip ïa kata ka jingkyntip. Ka jingbitar jong u te ka la meh buk, bad u la leit kiew sha ka ïing u kpa jong u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, ïa ka tnga u Samson la ai ha u lok jong u, ïa uba u la ñiew kum la u lok."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hynrei, hadien katto katne, hamar ka aïom ot Kew, u Samson u la leit khmih ïa la ka tnga bad iwei i khun blang; bad u la ong, “Ngan leit shapoh sha ka tnga jong nga sha ka kamra.” Hynrei, u kpa jong ka um shah ïa u ban rung shapoh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u kpa jong ka u la ong, “Nga la mut shisha ba me la isih noh ïa ka; namar kata, nga la ai ïa ka ha u lok jong me: ka para jong ka kam long kham bhabriew ban ïa ka? Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shim pli ïa ka.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Samson u la ong ha ki, “Ha kane ka por ngan khuid na ki Philistia, la ngan pynjulor ïa ki.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Samson u la leit bad u la kem laispah tylli ki myrsiang, bad u la shim ïa ki jingtbeh prew, te haba u la pynphai para tdong, u la buh ka jingtbeh prew hapdeng ar ar ki tdong baroh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ynda u la lah tbeh ïa kita ki prew, u la pyllait ïa ki sha ki lyngkha Kew jong ki Philistia, bad la ing khoit ki kyntem bad ïa u bym pat ot, bad ïa ki brisoh Olib ruh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hangta ki Philistia ki la ïa-ong, “Mano ba la leh ïa kane?” Ki la ong, “U Samson keiñ, u pyrsa kurim uta u nong Timnath, namar ba u la shim ïa ka tnga jong u, bad u la ai ïa ka ha u lok jong u.” Ki Philistia te ki la leit kiew buk, bad ki la thang ïa ka bad ïa u kpa jong ka da ka ding.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Samson u la ong ha ki, “Lada phi leh kum kane ka rukom, shisha ngan pynhiar kput halor jong phi, te hadien kata ngan sa iehnoh.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u la kawang ïa ki naphang da ka jingpynïap kaba khraw: te haba u la leit hiar, u la shong ha ka ar khap mawsiang Etam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, ki Philistia ki la leit kiew, bad ki la sher dara ha Judah, bad ki la phriang kylleng ha Lehi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ki Judah ki la ong te, “Balei phi la wan kiew pyrshah ïa ngi?” Ki te ki la ïathuh, “Ban khum ïa u Samson ngi la ïawan kiew, ban leh ïa u kumba u la leh ïa ngi.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hangta lai hajar ki rangbah Judah ki la leit hiar sha kata ka ar khap mawsiang Etam, bad ki la ong ïa u Samson, “Mem tip ba ki Philistia ki long ki nongsynshar halor jong ngi? kaei kane te ba me la leh ïa ngi?” Bad u la ong ïa ki, “Kumba ki la leh ïa nga, kumta nga la leh ïa ki.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki la ong ha u, “Ngi ïawan hiar ban khum ïa me, ba ngin ïoh ai noh ïa me ha ka kti ki Philistia.” Te u Samson u la ong ha ki, “To smai ha nga, ba phi hi phin ym pynïap ïa nga.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki te ki la kren ha u, ki da ong, “Em; hynrei, ngin shu khum skhem ïa me, bad ngin ai noh ïa me ha ka kti jong ki: hynrei shisha, ngin ym pynïap ïa me.” Te ki la khum ïa u da ki ar tylli ki tyllai thymmai, bad ki la wallam noh artet ïa u na uta u mawsiang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ynda u la poi sha Lehi, ki Philistia ki la ïarisa, haba ki la ïakynduh bad u: te U Mynsiem U Trai u la wan borbah halor jong u, bad kita ki tyllai kiba ha ki kti jong u ki la long kum u 'saihon ba la thang ha ka ding, bad ki jingkhum jong u ki la hap noh na ki kti jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la ïoh kawei ka shyieng ngab thymmai jong ka kadda, te haba u la kner ïa la ka kti, u la shim ïa ka, bad u la pom da ka shi hajar ki briew.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u Samson u la ong, “Da ka shyieng ngab ka kadda, ki kynton halor ki kynton, Da ka shyieng ngab ka kadda nga la pom shi hajar ki briew.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te haba u la lah kut kaba kren, u la bred noh ïa kata ka shyieng ngab na la ka kti; bad u la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “Ramath-lehi.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u la sliang thrang eh, bad u la kyrpad ïa U Trai, u la ong, “Me la ai ïa kane ka jingpyllait bakhraw da ka kti u shakri jong me: mynta te ngan ïap da kaba sliang, bad ngan hap ha ka kti jong kiba khlem otsher?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, U Blei u la pynpdang ïa kata ka them kaba ha Lehi, bad ka la mih um na ka; te ynda u la dih, ka la wan pat ka mynsiem jong u, bad u la phngain pat: namar kata, u la khot kyrteng ïa ka, “ka En-hakkore,” kaba ha Lehi, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u la bishar ïa ki Israel ha ki sngi ki Philistia arphew snem."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Samson u la leit sha Gasa, bad u la ïohi hangta ka nuti, bad u la rung shapoh sha ka.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> La ïathuh te ha ki nong Gasa, ki da ong, “U Samson u la wan shane.” Te ki la ker tawiar ïa u, bad ki la ap jar jar baroh shi miet ha ka khyrdop ka shnong, bad ki la ap jar jar baroh shi miet, ki da ong, “Ieh ha ban da shai, ynda kumta ngin sa pynïap ïa u.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Samson u la thiah haduh shiteng synñia, bad u la khie hamar shiteng synñia, bad u la bat khak ïa ki jingkhang ka khyrdop ka shnong bad shawkad, bad u la rat noh ïa ki, lem bad u narkhang bad ei ei, te haba u la kyntiew ïa ki ha ki tyrpeng jong u, u la bah ïa ki sha kliar u lum uba ha marpyrshah ka Hebron.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ka la jia hadien kata, ba u la ieit ïa kawei ka briew kaba ha them Sorek, kaba kyrteng ka Delilah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ki doloi ki Philistia te ki la wan kiew sha ka, bad ki la ong ha ka, “To ïapah ïa u, bad to khmih ha-ei ka borbah jong u ka shong, bad da kumno ka lad ngi lah ban jop ïa u, ba ngi lah ban khum ïa u ban pynshitom ïa u: bad ngin ai de ha pha uwei uwei na ngi khatwei spah ki sbai rupa.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ka Delilah ka la ong ha u Samson, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to ïathuh ïa nga ha-ei ka borbah jong me ka shong, bad da ei lah ban khum ïa me ban pynshitom ïa me.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Samson u la ong ïa ka, “Lada ki khum ïa nga da ki hynñiew tylli ki thri im ki bym pat ïap saw, te ngan sa tlot, bad ngan long kum uwei pat u briew.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, ki doloi ki Philistia ki la wallam ha ka hynñiew tylli ki thri im ki bym pat ïap saw, ka de ka la khum ïa u da ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ka la don ki nongap kiba ïa-ap ha ka kamra kham shapoh. Te ka la ong ha u, “Kine ki Philistia kin sa kem ïa me, ko Samson.” Te u la bthat ïa kita ki thri, kumba dkut u 'saihon haba u dei ïa ka ding. Kumta, ïa ka bor jong u ym shym la tip.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ka Delilah ka la ong ha u Samson, “Ha khmih, me la ibeiñ ïa nga, bad me la kren lamler ïa nga: nga kyrpad ïa me, to ïathuh ïa nga, da ei lah ban khum ïa me.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U te u la ong ha ka, “Lada kin tang shu khum ïa nga da ki tyllai thymmai ïa kiba ym shym la treikam, te ngan sa tlot, bad ngan long kum uwei pat u briew.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kumta ka Delilah ka la shim da ki tyllai thymmai, bad ka la khum ïa u da ki, bad ka la ong ha u, “Ki Philistia kin sa kem ïa me, ko Samson.” Hangta ruh kita ki nongap ki ïa-ap ha ka kamra kham shapoh. U te u la pyndkut ïa kita na ki kti kum u ksai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ka Delilah ka la ong ha u Samson, “Haduh mynta me la ibeiñ ïa nga, bad me la kren lamler ïa nga: to ïathuh ha nga, da ei lah ban khum ïa me?” U te u la ong ha ka, “Lada phan ïathain ïa kita ki jingkdor u 'ñiuh khlieh jong nga da kata ka jingthain.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ka la pynskhem ïa ka ha u snar, bad ka la ong ha u, “Ki Philistia kin sa kem ïa me, ko Samson.” Te u la khie joit na kaba ïohthiah, bad u la rong noh ïa u snar jong u bim, lem bad kata ka jingthain de.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ka te ka la ong ha u, “Kumno me lah ban ong, ‘Nga ieit ïa pha,’ haba ka dohnud jong me kam long ryngkat bad nga? me la ibeiñ ïa nga kumne la lai wat, ba mem shym la ïathuh ha nga ha-ei ka shong ka borbah jong me.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba ka la ïaipynsatia ïa u ha la ka sngi da la ki ktien, bad ka la pynbor ïa u, ka mynsiem jong u ka la pisa kum ban sa ïap.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u la ïathuh ha ka, ïa la ka dohnud baroh bad u la ong ïa ka, “Ka syrti kam shym la dei ïa ka khlieh jong nga; naba nga long u Nasar ha U Blei naduh ka kpoh ka kmie jong nga: lada yn khi ïa nga, te ka bor jong nga kan leit noh na nga, bad ngan sa tlot, bad ngan long kum uwei pat u briew.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba ka Delilah ka la ïohi ba u la ïathuh ha ka, ïa la ka dohnud baroh, ka la phah khot ïa ki doloi ki Philistia, ka da ong, “To wan kiew sa kane shi sien, naba u ïathuh ha nga ïa la ka dohnud baroh.” Ynda kumta, ki doloi ki Philistia ki la wan kiew sha ka, bad ki la wallam sbai ha la ki kti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ka la pynïohthiah ïa u ha ki khohsiew jong ka; bad haba ka la khot briew, ka la phah khi noh ïa ki hynñiew ki jingkdor ka khlieh jong u; bad ka la sdang ban pynshitom ïa u, bad ka bor jong u ka la kynriah noh na u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ka la ong ruh, “Ki Philistia kin sa kem ïa me, ko Samson.” U te u la khie joit na kaba ïohthiah, bad u la ong, “Ngan mih shabar kumba mynshuwa, bad ngan kynther ïa lade.” Hynrei, um shym tip ba U Trai u la kynriah na u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ki Philistia ki la kem ïa u, bad ki la khlaw noh ïa ki khmat jong u; bad ki la ïalam arsut ïa u sha Gasa, bad ki la khum ïa u da ki kynjri rnong; bad u la tylliat ha ka ïing byndi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, u shñiuh ka khlieh jong u, u la sdang ban mihpat hadien ba la khi ïa u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki doloi ki Philistia ki la ïalum lang ïa ka ban ainguh da ka jingkñia bakhraw ha u Dagon u blei jong ki, bad ban ïalehkmen: naba ki la ong, “U blei jong ngi u la ai noh ïa u Samson u nongshun jong ngi ha ka kti jong ngi.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Haba ki briew ki la ïohi ïa u te, ki la ïaroh ïa u blei jong ki: naba ki la ong, “U blei jong ngi u la ai noh ha ka kti jong ngi ïa u nongshun jong ngi bad u nongpynjot ïa ka ri jong ngi, uba la pynïap shibun na ngi.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te haba ki dohnud jong ki, ki la sngewbha, ki la ong, “To khot ïa u Samson ban long ka jingbiria ïa ngi.” Bad ki la khot ïa u Samson na ka ïing byndi; bad u la leh biria ha khmat jong ki: te ki la buh ïa u hapdeng ki rishot.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> U Samson te u la ong ha u khynnah uba bat ïa u na ka kti, “To shah ïa nga ba ngan ïoh tba ïa ki rishot kiba kyrshan ïa ka ïing, ba ngan ïoh shaniah ha ki.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kata ka ïing te ka la dap da ki shynrang bad kynthei; bad ki doloi ki Philistia baroh ki la don hangta; bad la don shalor ka ïing kumba lai hajar ki shynrang bad kynthei, kiba ïakhmih kai katba u Samson u la leh biria.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U Samson te u la kyrpad ïa U Trai, bad u la ong, “A Trai uba U Blei, nga duwai ïa me, to kynmaw ïa nga, bad to pynkhlaiñ ïa nga, nga duwai ïa me sa tang kane shi sien, A U Blei, ba ngan ïoh pynhiar kput shisyndon ha ki Philistia na ka bynta ki khmat jong nga baroh ar.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Samson u la bat ïa kita ki ar tylli ki rishot pdeng ha kiba la neh ka ïing, bad u la snoh ha ki, uwei da ka kti kamon, bad uwei da kadiang.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U Samson u la ong te, “To ngan ïap lem bad ki Philistia.” Te u la khun da la ka bor baroh; ka ïing te ka la ngat halor ki doloi, bad halor ki briew baroh kiba la don ha ka. Kumta, kita ki baïap kiba u la pynïap haba u la ïap ki la kham bun ban ïa kita ba u la pynïap mynba u dang im.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, ki para jong u bad ka ïing u kpa jong u baroh haba ki la leit hiar, ki la shim ïa u, bad ki la wallam noh ïa u, bad ki la tep ïa u hapdeng ka Sorah bad ka Eshtaol ha ka jingtep u Manoah u kpa jong u. Bad u la bishar ïa ki Israel arphew snem."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la don u briew na ri lum Ephraim, uba kyrteng “u Mikah”.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u la ong ha la ka kmie, “Kita ki khatwei spah shekel rupa ïa kiba la tuh na pha shaphang kiba pha la tim, bad ba pha la kren ruh ha kaba nga la ïohsngew, ha khmih, kata ka rupa ka don ha nga: nga la shim ma nga.” Ka kmie jong u te ka la ong, “To U Trai un kyrkhu ïa u khun jong nga.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u la ai pat ïa kita ki khatwei spah ki sbai rupa ha la ka kmie, ka kmie jong u te ka la ong, “Nga shisha nga pynkyntang ïa kata ka rupa ha U Trai na la ka kti na ka bynta u khun jong nga, ban mutdur bleithaw bad ban saiñdur bleithaw; te mynta, ngan ai noh ïa ka ha me.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba u la ai pat ïa uta u sbai ha la ka kmie, ka kmie jong u ka shim arspah sbai ka rupa, bad ka la ai ïa ki ha u nongsaiñ, uba na kita u la mut durblei bad u la thaw durblei: bad kita ki la don ha ka ïing u Mikah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te uta u briew, u Mikah keiñ, u la don ka ïing blei, bad u la thaw ïa ka ephod, bad ïa ki teraph, bad u la pynkyntang ïa uwei na ki khun jong u, ba un long u lyngdoh jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ha kita ki sngi, ym ju don syiem ha Israel: uwei uwei baroh la ju leh katba ibit hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te la don uwei u samla na Bethlehem Judah, na ka ïing Judah, uba long u Lebi, bad u la shong hangta.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad uta u briew u la leit mih noh na kata ka shnong, na Bethlehem Judah keiñ, ban leit shong kat shaba u shem: te katba u ïaid u la wan poi sha ka ri lum Ephraim sha ka ïing u Mikah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> U Mikah te u la ong ha u, “Nangno me la wan?” U te u la ong ha u, “Nga long u Lebi na Bethlehem Judah, bad nga leit shong kat shaba shem.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Mikah u la ong ha u, “To shong bad nga, bad to long u kpa bad u lyngdoh jong nga, te ngan ai ïa me shiphew ki sbai rupa shi snem shi snem, bad shi riam ki jaiñkup jaiñsem bad ka bam. Kumta, uta u Lebi u la rung shapoh.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad uta u Lebi u la sngewbha ban shong bad uta u briew, bad uta u samla u la long ïa u kum uwei na ki khun jong u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Mikah te u la pynkyntang ïa uta u Lebi, bad uta u samla u la long u lyngdoh jong u, bad u la don ha ka ïing u Mikah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, u Mikah u la ong, “Mynta nga tip ba U Trai un leh bha ïa nga, namar nga don u lyngdoh jong nga da u Lebi.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ha kita ki sngi, ym ju don syiem ha Israel: te ha kita ki sngi ka jaid u Dan ka la wad la ka ri kynti ban shong; naba haduh kata ka sngi, ym don ka ri kynti kaba la hap ha ki hapdeng ki jaid Israel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki khun u Dan ki la phah na ki kur jong ki, san ngut ki rangbah napdeng jong ki baroh, ki briew ki bashlur, na Sorah, bad na Eshtaol, ban syntiat ïa ka ri, bad ban jngoh ïa ka; ki la ong te ha ki, “Khie leit jngoh ïa kata ka ri:” bad ki la wan poi sha ri lum Ephraim, sha ka ïing u Mikah, bad ki la thiah basa hangta.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Haba ki la don hajan ka ïing u Mikah, ki la sngewthuh ïa ka ktien uta u samla u Lebi: te haba ki la phai shata ki la ong ha u, “Uei ba la wallam ïa me shane? bad me leh aïu ha kane ka jaka? bad aïu me don hangne?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U te u la ong ha ki, “Kumne u Mikah u leh bad nga, te u la ïakut nong ïa nga, bad nga long u lyngdoh jong u.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki la ong ha u, “Ngi kyrpad ïa me, to ïakylli na U Blei, ba ngin ïoh tip la kan bha ka jingleit jong ngi sha kaba ngi ïaid.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Uta u lyngdoh te u la ong ïa ki, “To leit ha kaba suk: ha khmat U Trai long ka lynti jong phi kaba phi ïaid.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, kita ki san ngut ki briew ki la leit noh, bad ki la wan poi sha Laish, bad ki la ïohi ïa ki briew kiba ha ka, kumno ki ju shong ha kaba suk, kum ka rukom ki nong Sidon, ha kaba suk bad khlem sumar; naba ym don mano mano ha kata ka ri uba don ka bor, uba lah ban pynlehrain ïa ki ha kaei kaei, bad ki jngai de na ki nong Sidon, bad kim ju ïadonkam badno badno ruh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki la ïawan sha la ki para ha Sorah bad Eshtaol: te kita ki para jong ki, ki la ong ha ki, “Kumno phi ong?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki la ong te, “To ïeng, ïa ngin ïaleit kiew ban ïaleh ïa ki: naba ngi la ïohi ïa kata ka ri, te, ha khmih, ka long ka babha eh: balei phi shu sngap? wat leh jaipdeh ïa ka ban leit rung ban ïoh ïa kata ka ri.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda phi leit, phin poi sha ki briew ba khlem sumar, bad kata ka ri ruh kaba khraw: naba U Blei u la ai ïa ka ha ka kti jong phi; ka jaka ka bym kyrduh ei ei katba don ha ka khyndew.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumta, hynriewspah ki rangbah ba la kieng atiar ïapom ki la ïamih nangta na ka jaid Dan, na Sorah bad na Eshtaol.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki la leit kiew ruh, bad ki la sher dara ha Kiriath-jearim, ha Judah: namar kata, ki la kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “Mahaneh-dan”, haduh kane ka sngi: ha khmih, ka don sha lyndet ka Kiriath-jearim.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nangta te ki la nang ïaid sha ri lum Ephraim, bad ki la wan sha ïing u Mikah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ki la ong kita ki san ngut ki rangbah kiba la leit ban syntiat ïa ka ri Laish, bad ki la ong de ha la ki para, “Phi tip ne em ba ha kine ki ïing don ka ephod, bad ki teraph, bad ka bleithaw ba la mutdur, bad ka durblei ba la saiñ? mynta te to pyrkhat kumno phi dei ban leh.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki la phai shata, bad ki la wan sha ka ïing uta u samla u Lebi, sha ïing u Mikah keiñ, bad ki la ïakhublei ïa u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kita ki hynriewspah ki rangbah ïa kiba la kieng atiar ïapom, kiba na ki khun u Dan, ki la ïeng hajan ka jingkhang ka khyrdop.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kita ki san ngut ki rangbah kiba la leit syntiat ïa kata ka ri ki la leit kiew, bad ki la rung shapoh shata, bad ki la shim ïa kata ka bleithaw ba la mutdur, bad ïa ka ephod, bad ïa ki teraph, bad ïa ka bleithaw ba la saiñ: uta u lyngdoh te u la ïeng hajan ka jingkhang ka khyrdop bad kita ki hynriewspah ki rangbah ba la kieng atiar ïapom,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba kine ki la leit shapoh ka ïing u Mikah, bad ki la shim ruh ïa ka dur bleithaw, bad ïa ka ephod, bad ïa ki teraph, bad ïa ka bleithaw ba la saiñ, uta u lyngdoh u la ong ha ki, “Phi leh aïu?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki te ki la ong ha u, “To sngap jar; bad to buh la ka kti ha la ka shyntur, bad to leit bad ngi, bad to long ïa ngi u kpa bad u lyngdoh: ka kham bha ïa me ban long lyngdoh ïa ka ïing uwei u briew, lane ban long lyngdoh ïa ka jaid bad ka kur ha Israel?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ka dohnud uta u lyngdoh ka la kmen, te u la shim ïa kata ka ephod, bad ïa ki teraph, bad ïa ka dur bleithaw, bad u la ïaid hapdeng u paidbah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, haba ki la phai ki la leit noh, bad ki la buh ha shuwa jong ki ïa ki khynnah bad ïa ki jingri bad ïa ki mar ki mata.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda ki la kham jngai na ka ïing u Mikah, ki rangbah kiba ha ki ïing kiba marjan ïing bad ka ïing u Mikah ki la ïalum lang, bad ki la lap ïa ki khun u Dan.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ki la pyrta ha ki khun u Dan. Ki te haba ki la phai la ki khmat, ki la ong ha u Mikah, “Me donkam aïu, ba me wan bad u paidbah katne?”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U te u la ong, “Phi la rah noh ïa ki blei ba nga la thaw, bad ïa uta u lyngdoh, bad phi la leit noh, te nga dang don aïu shuh? te kumno ba phi ong ïa nga, ‘Me donkam aïu?’ ”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki khun u Dan ki la ong ha u, “Wat ai ban ïohsngew shuh ïa ka ktien jong me hapdeng jong ngi, ïoh ba ki briew babitar kin kynrup ïa me, bad men duh ïa la ka jingim, bad ki jingim kiba ha ïing jong me de.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki khun u Dan te ki la leit sha la ka lynti: te haba u Mikah u la ïohi ba ki la kham don bor ban ïa u, u la leit phai noh sha la ïing.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ki la shim ïa kata kaba u Mikah u la lah shna bad ïa uta u lyngdoh uba u la don, bad ki la wan poi sha Laish, sha ki briew kiba suk bad khlem sumar, bad ki la pom ïa ki da ka syrti waitlam; bad ki la thang ïa ka shnong da ka ding.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te ym shym la don u nongpyllait, namar ka la jngai na Sidon, bad kim ju ïadonkam badno badno ruh; te ka la long ha ka them kaba don hajan Beth-rehob. Ki la tei ruh ïa kata ka shnong, bad ki la shong hangta.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ki la kyrteng ïa kata ka shnong “ka Dan”, kum ka kyrteng u Dan u kpa jong ki, ïa uba la kha ha u Israel: toi ka kyrteng jong kata ka shnong ha kaba mynnyngkong ka la long “ka Laish”.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ki khun u Dan ki la pynïeng na ka bynta ïa lade ïa kata ka dur bleithaw: bad u Jonathan, u khun u Gershom, u khun u Moses, ma u bad ki khun shynrang jong u ki la long ki lyngdoh ïa ka jaid Dan haduh ka sngi ka jingring mraw ïa kata ka ri.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kumta, ki la pynïeng ïa kata ka dur bleithaw jong u Mikah kaba u la thaw, baroh shi katta katba ka ïing U Blei ka la don ha Sheiloh."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha kita ki sngi, haba ym ju don syiem ha Israel, la don uwei u Lebi uba la shong ha ranab lum Ephraim, uba la ïoh tnga kliar na Bethlehem Judah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kata ka tnga kliar te ka la klim nalor jong u, bad ka la leit noh na u sha ka ïing u kpa jong ka sha Bethlehem Judah, bad ka la sah hangta saw bnai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U tnga jong ka te u la ïeng bad u la leit bud ïa ka ba un kren sngewbha ïa ka, ïa ka ban wallam pat ïa ka, u da don ruh bad la u shakri, bad shi jur ki kadda: ka te ka la wallam ïa u sha ïing u kpa jong ka: te haba u kpa kata ka samla u la ïohi ïa u, u la kmen ban ïashem bad u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u kthaw kurim jong u, u kpa kata ka samla, u la bat ïa u; bad u la sah bad u lai sngi: kumta, ki la ïabam ïadih, bad ki la shong basa hangta.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ha ka sngi ka basaw ki la khie la dang step, bad u la ïeng joit ban leit wan noh: u kpa kata ka samla te u la ong ha la u pyrsa kurim, “To pyntngen ïa la ka dohnud da bam kpu khyndiat, hadien kata te phin sa leit noh.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, ki la ïashong bad ki la ïabam ïadih lang baroh ar ngut: te u kpa kata ka samla u la ong ha uta u briew, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to sngewbha bad to sah baroh shi miet, to pynsngewbha ruh ïa la ka dohnud.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Uta u briew te u la ïeng ban leit noh; hynrei, u kthaw kurim jong u, u la kyrpad eh ïa u, u te u thiah pat hangta.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u la khie la dang step ha ka sngi ka basan ban leit noh; te u kpa kata ka samla u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to pyntngen ïa la ka dohnud, bad to sah ha ban da noh ka sngi;” te ki la ïabam, baroh ar ngut.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba uta u briew u la ïeng ban leit noh, ma u bad ka tnga kliar jong u, bad la u shakri, u kthaw kurim jong u, u kpa kata ka samla, u la ong ha u, “Ha khmih, mynta ka sngi ka la noh eh ïan, nga kyrpad ïa phi, to sah baroh shi miet: ha khmih, ka sngi kan sa sep, to thiah noh hangne, ba kan sngewbha ka dohnud jong me, te lashai phin sa leit mih dang step, ba phi lah ban poi sha la ïing.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, uta u briew um treh ban sah ha kata ka miet, hynrei, u la ïeng joit bad u la leit noh, bad u la poi ha pyrshah ka Jebus (kata ka long “ka Jerusalem”): te la don bad u ar tylli ki kadda ba la teh jin: ka tnga kliar jong u ruh ka la don lem bad u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda ki la poi hajan Jebus, ka la noh eh ka sngi; te uta u shakri, u la ong ha la u kynrad, “Ale, nga kyrpad ïa me, to ngin phai sha kane ka shnong ki Jebus, bad ngin thiah basa ha ka.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U kynrad jong u te u la ong ha u, “Ngin ym phai sha ka shnong u nongwei, ha kaba ym don ki khun Israel; hynrei, ngin da leit haduh Gibeah.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U la ong ruh ha la u shakri, “Ale, ïa ngin ïaleit hajan kawei na kine ki jaka; bad ngin thiah miet ha Gibeah, ne ha Ramah.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kumta, ki la ïaid noh bad ki la leit la ka lynti; te ka sngi ka la sep haba ki la poi hajan Gibeah, kaba dei jong ki Benjamin.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki la phai shata, ban thiah miet ha Gibeah: te haba u la leit hapoh u la shong ha ka lynti shnong: naba ym don ba khot ïing ïa ki ban thiah basa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te, ha khmih, la wan uwei u tymmen na la ka jingtrei na ka lyngkha ha ka por premmiet; uta u briew te uba na ri lum Ephraim, bad uba shong ha Gibeah: hynrei, ki briew kiba ha kata ka jaka ki long ki Benjamin.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te haba u la khmied la ki khmat, u la ïohi ïa uta u briew uba leit jingleit ha lynti ka shnong; bad uta u tymmen u la ong, “Shano men leit? bad nangno me wan?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U te u la ong ha u, “Ngi ïaleit na Bethlehem-judah sha khap ri lum Ephraim; nga uba nangta, bad nga la leit sha Bethlehem Judah: te mynta nga leit sha ïing U Trai; te ym don ba ïakhot ïing ïa nga.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, don phlang bad ka jingbam ïa ki kadda jong ngi; bad don kpu bad Waiñ ruh ïa nga bad ïa ka shakri jong me, bad ïa une u samla uba bad la ki shakri: ym don ei ei kaba duna.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Uta u tymmen u la ong te, “Suk me; la kumno kumno ai ba ki jingduna jong me baroh kin long halor jong nga; tang ba men ym thiah ha khyndew.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, u la wallam ïa u sha la ïing, bad u la ai jingbam ha kita ki kadda: bad ki la sum ïa la ki kjat, bad ki la bam ki la dih.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Katba ki la dang pynsngewbha ïa la ki dohnud, ha khmih, ki briew jong kata ka shnong, kiba na ki khun u Belial, ki la ker tawiar ïa kata ka ïing, ki da pduh ïa ka jingkhang; ki la kren te ha uta u trai ïing, uta u tymmen keiñ, ki da ong, “To pynmih noh ïa uta u briew uba la wan ha ïing jong me, ba ngin ïoh ithuh ïa u.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te uta u briew, u trai kata ka ïing, u la mih shabar sha ki, bad u la ong ha ki, “Em, ko para, nga kyrpad ïa phi, wat leh bymman katta katta; namar une u briew u la wan hapoh ka ïing jong nga, wat leh kane ka basniew.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ha khmih kane ka khun jong nga ka samla, bad ka tnga kliar jong u; ïa kine ngan wallam shabar mynta, bad to pynjahburom ïa ki, bad to leh bad ki katba ibit ma phi; hynrei, ha une u briew wat leh ka bymman kat kane.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, kita ki briew kim shahshkor ïa u: kumta, uta u briew u la shim ïa ka tnga kliar, bad u la ïalam ïa ka shabar sha ki: bad ki la ithuh ïa ka, bad ki la lehbeiñ ïa ka baroh shi miet haduh mynstep: te haba la sdang mih ka sngi, ki la pyllait noh ïa ka.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, kata ka briew ka la wan hamar ba shai byrngut ka sngi, bad ka la kyllon ha ka jingkhang ka ïing uta u briew ha kaba la don u kynrad jong ka, ha ban da shai.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te haba u kynrad jong ka u la khie mynstep, u la plie ïa ki jingkhang jong ka ïing, bad u la mih shabar ïa ka ban leit noh; te, ha khmih, kata ka briew ka tnga kliar jong u ka la lah kyllon ha ka jingkhang ka ïing, bad ki kti jong ka halor u maw jingryngkang.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U la ong te ha ka, “To khie joit, ba ngin ïaleit noh;” hynrei, ym don ba phai ktien: ynda kumta, u la kyntiew ïa ka halor ka kadda; bad haba uta u briew u la ïeng u la leit sha la ka jaka.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te ynda u la wan poi ha la ïing, u la shim ïa ka tari, bad u la bat ïa la ka tnga kliar, bad u la bynta ïa ka katba kum ki shyieng jong ka khat-ar dkhot, bad u la phah ïa ka sha ki phang ki Israel baroh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ka la long kumta, ba baroh kiba la ïohi ïa kata ki la ong, “Ym shym la leh lymne ïohi ka kam kat kane naduh kata ka sngi ba ki khun Israel ki la wan mih noh na ka ri Ijipt haduh kane ka sngi: to pyrkhat ïa kane, to ïapyrkhat lem, bad to kren.”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, ki khun Israel baroh ki la mih noh, bad u paidlang u la ïalum lang kum kawei, naduh Dan haduh Beer-sheba, lem bad ka ri Gilead, sha U Trai ha Mispah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki rangbah jong uta u paidbah baroh, ki jong ki jaid Israel baroh keiñ, ki la ïa-mihpaw ha ka jingïalang u paidlang jong U Blei, sawspah hajar ki rangbah ba ïaleh na tbian kiba rah wait.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> (Ki khun u Benjamin te ki la bna ba ki khun Israel ki la lah leit kiew sha Mispah.) Te ki khun Israel ki la ïa-ong, “To ïathuh ha ngi, kumno ka la jia kane ka jingbymman?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te uta u Lebi, u tnga kata ka kynthei ba la pynïap, u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Nga la poi sha Gibeah jong u Benjamin, ma nga bad la ka tnga kliar, ban thiah miet.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki nong Gibeah ki la ïeng ïaleh ïa nga, bad ki la ker tawiar ïa ka ïing pyrshah ïa nga mynmiet; ki la mut ban pynïap ïa nga, bad ïa ka tnga kliar jong nga ki la khñiot, bad ka la ïap.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba nga la shim ïa ka tnga kliar jong nga, nga la ot dkhot ïa ka, bad nga la phah ïa ka ha ka ri jong ka ri kynti ki khun Israel baroh: naba ki la leh kaba ijli bad ka bymman ha Israel.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ha khmih, phi ki khun Israel, phi baroh, to pyni hangne ïa la ka jingmut bad ïa la ka jingpyrkhat.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u paidlang baroh u la ïeng kawei, u da ong, “Ngin ym leit mano mano na ngi sha la ka ïingjaiñ, lymne ngin ym leit phai mano mano na ngi sha la ïing.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mynta te, kane ka long kaba ngin leh ïa ka Gibeah; ngin leit kiew ban ïaleh ïa ka da ka jingkhalai;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na ki shispah ngut ngin shim shiphew ngut na ki jaid Israel baroh, bad na ki shi hajar ngut shispah, bad na ki shiphew hajar ngut shi hajar, ban rah jingbam ïa u paidbah, ba ynda ki la wan sha Gibeah jong u Benjamin, kin ïoh leh katba kum kata ka jingbymman baroh ïa kaba ki la leh ha Israel.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumta, ki rangbah Israel baroh ki la ïalang ban ïaleh ïa kata ka shnong, ba la syrdoh lang kum kawei.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki jaid Israel ki la phah briew lyngba ka jaid Benjamin baroh, ki da ong, “Kaei kane ka jingbymman kaba la long hapdeng jong phi?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Namar kata te, to ai noh ïa kita ki briew, ki khun u Belial, kiba ha Gibeah, ba ngin ïoh pynïap ïa ki, bad ngin pynduh noh ïa ka basniew na Israel.” Hynrei, ki Benjamin kim sngap ïa ka ktien ki para jong ki, ki khun Israel.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki khun u Benjamin ki la ïalum lang na ki shnong ki shnong sha Gibeah, ïa ka ban leit ïaleh thma ïa ki khun Israel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki la kheiñ ïa ki khun u Benjamin ha kata ka sngi na ki shnong ki shnong arphew hynriew hajar ki rangbah kiba rah wait, nalor ki nong Gibeah ïa kiba la kheiñ hynñiewspah kiba la khara.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hapdeng une u paidbah baroh la don hynñiewspah ngut ki riewkadiang kiba khara; uwei pa uwei u lah ban shat maw kat i shñiuh ruh, im lait.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ïa ki rangbah Israel, nalor ki Benjamin, la kheiñ sawspah hajar ngut kiba rah wait: kine baroh ki la long ki nongïapom.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la ïaïeng, bad ki la ïaleit kiew sha Bethel, bad ki la ïakylli na U Blei; ki la ong ruh, “Uno u ban leit kiew nyngkong na ka bynta jong ngi ban ïaleh thma ïa ki khun u Benjamin?” U Trai te u la ong, “U Judah un leit kiew nyngkong.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki khun Israel te haba ki la khie joit mynstep, ki la sher dara ban ïaleh ïa ka Gibeah.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u paidbah Israel u la leit ban ïaleh thma ïa u Benjamin; bad u paidbah Israel u la khreh riang la ka thma ban ïaleh ïa ki ha Gibeah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki khun u Benjamin ki la mih noh te na Gibeah, bad ki la pynïap noh thiaw na ki Israel ha kata ka sngi arphew ar hajar ki rangbah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad uta u paidbah, u paidbah Israel keiñ, u la pynshlur ïa lade, bad ki la khreh pat riang ïa ka thma ha kajuh ka jaka ha kaba ki la khreh ha ka sngi nyngkong.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> (Te ki khun Israel ki la ïaleit kiew bad ki la ïam ha khmat U Trai ha ban da la janmiet; bad ki ïakylli ïa U Trai, ki da ong, “Ngan leit kiew pat ban ïaleh thma ïa ki khun u Benjamin u para jong nga?” U Trai te u la ong, “Leit kiew ban ïaleh ïa u.”)",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la ïawan hajan ban ïaleh ïa ki khun u Benjamin ha ka sngi ka ba-ar.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ki Benjamin ki la mih noh de na Gibeah ban ïaleh ha ka sngi ka ba-ar, bad ki la pynïap thiaw na ki khun Israel sa khatphra hajar ki rangbah; kine baroh kiba rah wait.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, ki khun Israel baroh, bad u paidbah baroh, ki la ïaleit kiew, bad ki la wan sha Bethel, ki la ïam ruh, bad ki la shong hangta ha khmat U Trai, bad ki la shah jingit ha kata ka sngi ha ban da la janmiet; bad ki la ainguh da ki jingainguh thang bad ki jingainguh pynïasuk ruh ha khmat U Trai.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la ïakylli ïa U Trai, (naba ka synduk ka jutang U Blei ka la don hangta ha kita ki sngi,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad u Phinehas, u khun u Eleasar, u khun u Aaron, u la ïeng ha khmat jong ka ha kita ki sngi,) ki da ong, “Ngan dang leit shuh sha ka thma ïa ki khun u Benjamin u para jong nga, ne ngan keiñ noh?” Te U Trai u la ong, “Khie leit; namar lashai ngan ai noh ïa u ha ka kti jong me.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la buh ïa kiba ker kdong ïa ka Gibeah baroh sawdong.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la ïaleit kiew ban ïaleh ïa ki khun u Benjamin ha ka sngi ka balai, bad ki la khreh riang ban ïaleh ïa ka Gibeah, kumba mynshuwa.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad ki khun u Benjamin ki la mih ruh ban ïaleh ïa uta u paidbah bad la ring kyrpah ïa ki na shnong; ki te ki la sdang ban pom bad ban pynïap na uta u paidbah, kumba laiphew ngut na ki Israel, kumba mynshuwa, ha ki lynti bah, na kita kawei ka leit poi sha Bethel bad kata kawei sha Gibeah, ha lyngkha.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ki khun u Benjamin ki la ïa-ong, “La jop ïa ki ha khmat jong ngi, kumba ha ka banyngkong.” Hynrei, ki khun Israel ki la ïa-ong, “To ngin ïaphet, bad ngin ïaring kyrpah ïa ki na shnong sha ki lynti bah.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ki rangbah Israel baroh ki la ïeng noh na la ka jaka, bad ki la ïakhreh riang ha Baal-tamar: bad kiba ker kdong na ki Israel ki la mih ruh buk na la ka jaka, na shaphang sepngi ka Geba keiñ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad ki la wan ïaleh ïa ka Gibeah shiphew hajar ngut kiba la kynsai na ki Israel baroh, bad ka thma ka la jur eh: hynrei, kim shym tip ba ka basniew kan sa lap ïa ki.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te U Trai u la jop ïa u Benjamin ha khmat ki Israel; bad ki khun Israel ki la pynïap na u Benjamin ha kata ka sngi arphew san hajar bad shispah ngut: kine baroh kiba la rah wait.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kumta, ki khun u Benjamin ki la ïohi ba dang pynïap ïa ki: naba ki briew Israel ki la ai jaka ïa ki Benjamin, namar ki la shaniah ïa kita kiba ker kdong ïa kiba ki la lah buh ban ïaleh ïa ka Gibeah.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kita kiba ker kdong te ki la pynkloi bad ki la tur ha Gibeah; bad kita kiba ker kdong ki la nang wan hajan, bad ki la pom ïa ka shnong baroh da ka syrti waitlam.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te ka dak ba la ïabuh hapdeng ki rangbah Israel bad kita kiba ker kdong ka la long, ba kin pynkiew u lyoh tdem bakhraw na kata ka shnong.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te ki rangbah Israel ki la phai ha ka thma, bad ki Benjamin ki la sdang ban pom bad ban pynïap na ki Israel kumba laiphew ngut: naba ki la ong, “Shisha la jop ïa ki ha khmat jong ngi, kum ha ka jingïaleh ka banyngkong.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Hynrei, haba u lyoh u la sdang ban ïeng na kata ka shnong kum u rishot tdem, ki Benjamin ki la khmih shadien jong ki, te, ha khmih, ka shnong baroh kawei ka la leit kiew tdem sha bneng.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te ki rangbah Israel ki la phai, bad ki briew Benjamin ki la lyngngoh ngaiñ: naba ki la ïohi ba ka basniew ka la lah lap ïa ki.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Namar kata, ki la phai noh na khmat ki rangbah Israel sha ka lynti ka ri khlaw; hynrei, ka jingïaleh ka la beh roit roit ïa ki; bad kita kiba la mih na ki shnong ki la pynïap ïa ki hapdeng jong ki.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ki la ker tawiar ïa ki Benjamin baroh sawdong, ki la beh ïa ki, ki la ïuh roit ïa ki ha ki jaka shongthait jong ki, haduh marpyrshah ka Gibeah shaphang kaba mih ka sngi.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Bad la kyllon na ki Benjamin khatphra hajar ngut; kine baroh ki rangbah bashlur.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te haba ki la phai ki la phet ïap sha ka ri khlaw sha u mawsiang Rimmon: bad ki la khar na ki ha ki lynti bah san hajar ngut; bad ki la nang beh roit shi roit ïa ki haduh Gidom, bad ki la pynïap na ki ar hajar ngut.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Kumta, baroh kiba la kyllon ha kata ka sngi na ki Benjamin ki la long arphew san hajar ngut kiba rah wait; kine baroh ki rangbah bashlur.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Hynrei, hynriewspah ngut ki la phai bad ki la phet ïap sha ri khlaw u mawsiang Rimmon, bad ki la shong ha u mawsiang Rimmon saw bnai.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Ki rangbah Israel te ki la phai pat ha ki khun u Benjamin, bad ki la pom ïa ki da ka syrti waitlam, ïa ka shnong baroh kawei, bad ïa ki jingri, bad ïa baroh kat kaba ki shem: ïa ki shnong baroh ruh kat kiba ki la shem ki la thang ruh."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki rangbah Israel ki la lah smai ha Mispeh, ki da ong, “Uno uno ruh na ngi un ym buh kurim ïa la ka khun ha u Benjamin.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u paidbah u la ïawan sha Bethel, bad u la shong hangta haduh ba la janmiet ha khmat U Blei, bad ki la kyang, bad ki la ïam eh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ki la ong ruh, “A Trai, uba U Blei ki Israel, balei ba kane ka la jia ha Israel, ba ha kane ka la duna kawei ka jaid ha Israel?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te kum lashai, u paidbah u la khie dang step, bad haba ki la tei ïa ka duwan hangta, ki la ainguh da ki jingainguh thang bad ki jingainguh pynïasuk.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la ïa-ong, “Uei hapdeng ki jaid Israel baroh u bym shym la wan kiew lem bad u paidlang sha U Trai?” Naba ki la pynlong ïa ka jingsmai bajur shaphang uta u bym shym wan kiew sha U Trai ha Mispah, ki la ong, “Ïa uta yn pynïap shisha.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la kylla-ka-bamut na ka bynta u Benjamin u para jong ki, ki la ong ruh, “La pynduh ïa kawei ka jaid na Israel ha kane ka sngi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kumno ngin leh ban pynïoh tnga ïa kita kiba dang sah, haba ngi la smai ha U Trai ba ngin ym buh kurim ha ki na ki khun kynthei jong ngi?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ki la ong, “Uei uba don na ki jaid Israel u bym shym wan kiew sha U Trai ha Mispah?” Te, ha khmih, ym shym don ba wan uwei na Jabesh-gilead sha ka dara ha u paidlang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Naba haba la kheiñ ïa u paidbah, ha khmih, ym shym don uwei na ki Jabesh-gilead hangta.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u paidbah u la phah shata khat-ar hajar ngut na ki bashlur tam, bad u la hukum ïa ki, u da ong, “To khie leit pom ïa ki nong Jabesh-gilead da ka syrti waitlam, bad kynthei bad khynnah.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kane ka long kaba phin leh; phin pynduh khoit ïa u shynrang baroh, bad ïa ka kynthei baroh kaba la ïoh tnga.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki la shem hapdeng ki nong Jabesh-gilead sawspah ngut ki theisotti samla, ki bym shym la ithuh ïa u briew da kaba la thiah bad u: bad ki la wallam ïa ki sha ka dara ha Sheiloh, kaba don ha ka ri Kanaan.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u paidbah baroh u la phah bad u la kren ha ki khun u Benjamin kiba don ha u mawsiang Rimmon, bad ban pynbna ka jingïasuk ha ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki Benjamin ki la wan phai ha kata ka por; ki te ki la ai ha ki, ïa kita ki kynthei ïa kiba ki la ri im na ki kynthei jong ka Jabesh-gilead: la kumta ruh kim pat dap ïa ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u paidbah u la kylla-ka-bamut na ka bynta u Benjamin, namar ba U Trai u la lah pynlong ïa ka jingïapait ha ki jaid Israel.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, ki tymmen basan u paidbah ki la ïa-ong, “Kumno ngin leh ban pynïoh tnga ïa kita kiba dang sah, namar ba la pynduh ïa ki kynthei na Benjamin?”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ki la ong te, “Ka dei ban don ri kynti ïa kita kiba la lait na u Benjamin, ba yn ym pyndam noh ïa kawei ka jaid na Israel.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, ngi ngim lah ban buh kurim ha ki na ki khun kynthei jong ngi:” namar ki khun Israel ki la lah smai, ki da ong, “Long ba la tim ïa uta u ban buh kurim ha u Benjamin.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki la ong te, “Ha khmih, ka don Ka Jingkhawai Niam jong U Trai man la ka snem ha Sheiloh, kaba shaphang shatei na Bethel, shaphang mihngi ka lynti bah kaba leit kiew na Bethel sha Shekhem, bad shaphang shathie na Lebonah.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki la hukum ïa ki khun u Benjamin, ki da ong, “To khie leit thap ha ki brisoh Waiñ;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> to khmih ruh, te ha khmih, lada ki khun kynthei jong ka Sheiloh ki mih noh ban shad ha ki jingshad, ynda kumta, phin mih noh na kita ki brisoh Waiñ, bad to uwei uwei baroh un kem ïa ka ban long tnga ïa u na ki khun kynthei jong ka Sheiloh, bad to leit noh sha ka ri Benjamin.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te haba ki kpa jong ki lane ki hynmen jong ki kin wan mudui ha ngi, ngin ong ha ki, ‘To ai sngewbha ïa ki ha ngi: namar ha ka thma ngim shym la buh na ka bynta uwei uwei u briew ïa ka tnga jong u: lymne phim shym ai ïa ki ha ki; lada kumta phi la rem mynta.’ ”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki khun u Benjamin ki la leh kumta, bad ki la shim tnga ha ki, katba kum ka jingkheiñ jong ki, na kita kiba la shad, kiba ki la kem noh: te haba ki la leit ki la wan phai sha la ka ri kynti, bad ki la tei ïa ki shnong, bad ki la shong ha ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la leit noh nangta ha kata ka por, u briew baroh sha la ka jaid sha la ka kur, bad ki la mih noh nangta uwei uwei baroh sha la ka ri kynti.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ha kita ki sngi, ym ju don syiem ha Israel: uwei uwei baroh u la leh katba u ibit hi."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;